(23, 0, 'Ministry of Land Reform and Management (MoLRM),', 'ministry-of-land-reform-and-management-molrm', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.molrm.gov.np/', '/uploads/ourclients/nheicc(1).png', NULL, NULL, '<p>Ministry of Land Reform and Management (MoLRM), being the core ministry looking after the land administration and management activities, is responsible for ensuring efficient and effective administration and sustainable management of available land resources. It is also the prime responsibility of the ministry to provide effective and efficient service delivery to the general public. Furthermore, ensuring the availability of all kinds of geo-information products, which is the foundation of land administration and management activities, is the other principal responsibility of the ministry. The Ministry has the following functions as mentioned in the work division regulation, 2064 of the Government of Nepal</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:12:52', 1),
