(25, 0, 'TechnoHub USA', 'technohub-usa', NULL, NULL, 'http://technohubusa.com/', '/uploads/ourclients/techno.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Information Technology needs can often be confusing, it&#39;s dynamic and overwhelming. Techno Hub is one-stop solution for all your ventures in the booming IT industry. Technology is our business and we specialize in providing high quality services at affordable prices. Our company is at your beck-and-call, ready and eager to assist you in any sort of IT business scenario.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Be it website management, software development or IT courses and trainings we will guide you to help solve real world technology issues. Venturing into new territory can be intimidating, which is exactly when we bring our expertise and deep understanding to resolve the challenges you face. We are a reliable organization that consistently delivers high quality results. We have a deep focus on innovation and will provide tailored solutions based on your requirements.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:12:52', 1),
