(17, 2, 1, 'devicon-php-plain colored', '', 'Advanced PHP Training in Nepal', 'Advanced PHP Training', 'Advanced PHP Training', 'Advanced PHP Training in Nepal', 'Web Application Development with Framework Training (PHP/MySQL)', 'advanced-php-mysql-training-in-nepal', 'Advanced PHP Training in Nepal | Advanced PHP/MySQL Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'php training in nepal, advanced php training in nepal, web development php training in nepal, php training institute in nepal, php training in kathmandu', 'Take advanced PHP/MySQL Training at Broadway Infosys. Rated as Best PHP/MySQL Training Institute in Kathmandu Nepal. Learn with Industry Experts & become web app developer.', '', 'advanced-php-programming', '<h1>Courses Outline-Advance PHP/MYSQL</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>This PHP course is designed to enable beginner level web developers and others with limited programming experience to build dynamic database driven e-commerce web sites using PHP programming language. Since PHP is a rich and task-specific language, the course covers the most important range of functions in depth, and equips delegates to understand the remaining less essential aspects. At the instructor&#39;s discretion, training material modules may be omitted if the pace is slightly slower than anticipated. PHP is Open Source and Cross Platform, running on UNIX, Linux, MS Windows, Apple Mac, AS/400 and more, and is often used with an OS-CP database and web server such as MySQL and Apache. At the end of the course, student will be able to create their own database driven project.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"heading-title sub-cat\">Courses Outline-Advance PHP/MYSQL</h2>\r\n\r\n<h4>Web Development Fundamentals</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Introduction to Web Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding HTML Markup</li>\r\n	<li>Introduction to HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Exploring Domains, Web Hosting, Web Protocols like HTTP, FTP</li>\r\n	<li>Introduction to CSS</li>\r\n	<li>Introduction and difference between Server Side and 