(46, 5, 1, '', '/uploads/courses/1487854833.png', 'Advanced Magento Training in Nepal', 'Advanced Magento Training', 'Magento Advance', 'Magento Advanced Training in Nepal', '', 'magento-advanced-training-in-nepal', 'Advanced Magento Training in Nepal | Magento Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'magento training in nepal, advanced magento training in nepal, magento ecommerce development training, magento cms training', 'Take advanced Magento training at Broadway Infosys. Rated as Best Magento ecommerce institute in Kathmandu Nepal. Training by industry experts & 100% proficiency.', '', 'https://broadwayinfosys.com/advanced-magento-training-nepal.php', '<h1 class=\"heading-title\">Magento Advance</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Magento is a very powerful and fast growing ecommerce script, created by Varien. It is an open-source platform using Zend PHP and MySQL databases. Magento offers great flexibility through its modular architecture, is completely scalable and has a wide range of control options that its users appreciate.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Topics Covered in Magento</h4>\r\n\r\n<h4>Part 1</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fundamentals</li>\r\n	<li>Magento module-based architecture</li>\r\n	<li>Magento directory structure</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration XML</li>\r\n	<li>Functional and Factory class groups</li>\r\n	<li>Class overrides on Magento</li>\r\n	<li>Event Observer</li>\r\n	<li>Methods to resolve</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Part 2</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Application Initialization</li>\r\n	<li>Front Controllered.</li>\r\n	<li>URL Rewrite</li>\r\n	<li>Request Routing</li>\r\n	<li>Module Initialization</li>\r\n	<li>Design and layout initialization</li>\r\n	<li>Structure of block templates</li>\r\n	<li>Flushing data (outputs)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Part 3</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Template Structure</li>\r\n	<li>Block Structure</li>\r\n	<li>Blocks</li>\r\n	<li>Layout XML schema</li>\r\n	<li>Layout and CMS</li>\r\n	<li>Pass variables from layout to block1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"bo