(49, 0, 1, 'devicon-python-plain colored', '/uploads/courses/python.png', 'Python & Django Training in Nepal', 'Python & Django Training ', 'Python & Django Training ', 'Python Training in Nepal', 'Python & Django Training in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'python-django-training-in-nepal', 'Python Training In Nepal | Python Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'python training in nepal, python django training in nepal', 'Learn python at Broadway Infosys, Nepal. Rated as best python Training Institute. Learn dynamic language for web development, big data, science & scripting', '', 'https://broadwayinfosys.com/python-training-in-nepal.php', '<h1 class=\"heading-title\">Courses Outline- Web Development with Python And Django</h1>\r\n\r\n<h4>Python</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>- Overview</li>\r\n	<li>Environmnt setup (Virtual env) * Linux is must</li>\r\n	<li>Basic syntax</li>\r\n	<li>Variable types, basic operators</li>\r\n	<li>Numbers, string</li>\r\n	<li>List, tuples, dictionary</li>\r\n	<li>Decision making</li>\r\n	<li>Loops</li>\r\n	<li>Date and time</li>\r\n	<li>Function</li>\r\n	<li>Module</li>\r\n	<li>Class and objects</li>\r\n	<li>Regex</li>\r\n	<li>Project with python</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Django</h4>\r\n\r\n<h4>Django Basic</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Introduction</li>\r\n	<li>MVT pattern</li>\r\n	<li>Models</li>\r\n	<li>Forms</li>\r\n	<li>Views</li>\r\n	<li>Templates, urls</li>\r\n	<li>Database query, database relationship</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Django Intermediate</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>User authentication</li>\r\n	<li>Logging</li>\r\n	<li>Start of the project</li>\r\n	<li>Migrations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>Django Advance</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Using singlas</li>\r\n	<li>Using celery and rabbitmq to process long running task</li>\r\n	<li>Unit testing</li>\r\n	<li>Project completionS</li>\r\n	<li>(Note: - 1 week extra should be provided for basic linux syntax)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 3 Months<br />\r\n<strong>Career Option:</strong> Python Programmer<br />\r\n<strong>Pre-requisites:</strong> A basic understanding of web design or fundamental programming Language</p>\r\n', '<h2>Python Training in Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Broadway Infosys offers special Python training courses in Nepal as it is considered as one of the popular programming languages that is attracting large pool of developers worldwide. The giants like Google, Yahoo and Amazon are using Python for their special projects and this has further inspired many developers to learn this programming language in Nepal</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Course Highlights</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Python training course has been designed for aspiring developers with some level or no prior programming experience. The courses range from basic to advanced level. The course is all about familiarizing the trainees with simpler and smarter ways to develop interactive web applications using Python. At the end of the training, students need to undertake a project work to develop interactive application using Python.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits of Python Training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Highly qualified and experienced Python instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Availability of sufficient training resources</li>\r\n	<li>Several Python developers trained at Broadway already working in top companies</li>\r\n	<li>Proficiency in dealing with Big Data analytics</li>\r\n	<li>Regular interaction among growing community of Python developers</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarizing with code efficiency in developing wide range of applications using Python</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Syllabus Outline</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Python Training course covers the following (but not limited to) syllabus:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Introduction to Python</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding of variables and identifiers, standard types and operators</li>\r\n	<li>Decision making, sequential data types, dictionaries, loops and functions</li>\r\n	<li>Modules and packages, object oriented Python</li>\r\n	<li>File processing and Exception Handling</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Python</li>\r\n	<li>Project work on Python</li>\r\n	<li>Project Evaluation and Feedback from experts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>As the leading companies around the world have started using Python for their projects the developers with Python skills can expect plenty of opportunities to work in innovative and high paying projects. Please register yourself for our upcoming Python training session to expand your programming portfolio. Our instructors are excited to guide you along the journey of Python Programming.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '', '2 Months', '', '', '', '<h3><strong>Web Development With Python &amp; Django</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nCourses Outline:- Python &amp; Django</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Introduction to Python and Django Framework</strong>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Overview</li>\r\n		<li>Requirement Installation &amp; Setup</li>\r\n		<li>Python Shell</li>\r\n		<li>Script Execution</li>\r\n		<li>Standard Library&rsquo;s</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Variables and Identifiers</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Identifiers</li>\r\n		<li>Variables</li>\r\n		<li>Naming Conventions</li>\r\n		<li>Python Keywords</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Standard Types (Built-in)</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Numbers</li>\r\n		<li>Strings</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Operators</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Basic Mathematic Operator</li>\r\n		<li>Operator Precedence</li>\r\n		<li>Comparison Operator</li>\r\n		<li>Logical (and, or, not) Operator</li>\r\n		<li>Identity (is, is not) operator</li>\r\n		<li>Membership (in, not in) Operator</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Decision Making</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>If, else, elif</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sequential Data Types</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>List</li>\r\n		<li>Tuples</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Dictionaries</strong>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Dictionary Operators / Functions</li>\r\n		<li>Iterating (Lists from/to Dictionary)</li>\