tance, use date api(ex: JodaTime library. There should be at least two form with CRUD operations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>WEB:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>No1: Show Spring RMI demo</strong><br />\r\n<strong>No2: Spring MVC web demo</strong><br />\r\n<strong>No3: Hibernate Separate demo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h1>Final Project:</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Integrated Web Project: Spring MVC Web, Hibernate JDBC, Maven, HTML Form, Validation, Date api, Session handling, filter, JDBC Crud Operation. Teacher will help to create mock project which contain spring, hibernate and maven. Student will finish up further requirement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;2 Months<br />\r\n<strong>Career Option:</strong>&nbsp;Java Programmer<br />\r\n<strong>Pre-requisites :</strong>Students attending Java training course should have basic knowledge of HTML, CSS, XML, SQL &amp; Core java</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'https://broadwayinfosys.com/java-training-package-nepal.php', 56, '2017-05-18 13:03:26', 1),
