(69, 3, 1, 'devicon-dot-net-plain colored', NULL, 'C# Training in Nepal', 'C# Training', 'C# Training', 'C# Training in Nepal', 'C#.net Training with .Net Training Package in Kathmndu, Nepal', 'c-sharp-training-in-nepal', 'C# Training in Nepal | C#.net training in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'c# training in nepal, c#.net training in nepal, c sharp training in nepal', 'Learn c#.net Training at Broadway Infosys. Rated as Best dot net Training Institute in Kathmandu Nepal. Training by Industry Experts & 100% proficiency.', '', NULL, NULL, '<h2>C# .NET Training in Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This course has been designed for beginners as well as individuals with no prior programming experience but interested to learn C#. &nbsp;This training not only provides familiarity with C# and its wider implications but also prepares the students to take on other programming languages such as Java, Objective &ndash;C . After the successful completion of C# training, the students are ready to write programs on .NET framework.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Course highlights</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Understanding &nbsp;basic concepts of C# and .Net framework</li>\r\n	<li>Declaration, initialization and manipulation of variables</li>\r\n	<li>Enough coding exercises for practical knowledge</li>\r\n	<li>Learning installation of Visual Studio to develop in C#</li>\r\n	<li>Creation of custom classes</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding inheritance</li>\r\n	<li>Understand how to handle exceptions and manage data collections</li>\r\n	<li>Learning other important programming skills</li>\r\n	<li>Project Work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits of C# .NET training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Highly experienced instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Career-oriented training courses</li>\r\n	<li>Self-sufficient training labs</li>\r\n	<li>Consistent practical classes to sharpen the programming skills</li>\r\n	<li>Regular guidance from industry experts</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to network with several .NET community members</li>\r\n