(77, 9, 0, '', '/uploads/courses/1487854335.png', 'IT Training in Nepal for SEE Students', 'IT Training in Nepal for SEE Students', 'IT Training for SEE & SLC Appeared Students ', 'IT Training for SEE & SLC Appeared Students', 'Computer Training Courses after SEE & SLC', 'it-training-for-see-slc-appeared-students', 'Computer Training for SEE and SLC Students | IT Courses Training Program for SEE & SLC Appeared Students', 'computer training for SEE students in Nepal, it training for see students, slc students computer training', 'Enroll into practical computer training program specially organized for SEE, SLC appeared students. Contact us today and book your seat for upcoming classes.', '', NULL, NULL, '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal has been known as a leading IT Training and development company in Nepal for last few years. More than thousands of IT and Management students have successfully completed their IT and software training programs and most of them are currently working at different IT companies thereby developing and enhancing their Careers in IT sector. We concentrate more on providing practical/project based training programs to the students from working and experienced IT experts and professionals. In today&rsquo;s competitive era, it is quite difficult to get a good job, also sustain and grow in the existing job. One of the reasons could be lack of soft skills. We have researched and understood this fact and therefore have been providing soft skill training to interested students from any sector from management and soft skill experts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe that today&rsquo;s SEE and S.L.C students are tomorrow&rsquo;s leaders and experts. Thus, the time gap between the completion of S.E.E and S.L.C exams and result is very important and should be utilized productively. Whatever the decision be of students regarding the subjects they select or Careers they target after result, proper skills in IT is very essential in every sector they wish to work. IT skills are an aid to whatever they do and an additional benefit in their studies and workplace. Every year, we have been bringing out different and innovative plans for the S.E.E and S.L.C students. We provide the IT courses that are relevant in different NGOs, INGOs, financial institutions and corporate houses.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '<h2>Courses we provide:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#tab1\">IT Training</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#tab2\">Softskill Training</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#basiccomputer\">Basic Computer Training (Practical)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#graphics\">Certificate in Graphics Design</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#\">Certificate in Advertisement Design</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#webdesin\">Certificate in Website Design ( Project Base)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#cplus\">C, C++ Programming</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/computer-training-for-slc-appeared-studsnts.php#php\">Certificate in PHP/MYSQL</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><a name=\"basiccomputer\">Basic Computer Training</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Windows</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage proper folder structure to store files in order</li>\r\n	<li>Searching files</li>\r\n	<li>Setting user privilege based on the user type</li>\r\n	<li>Installing and Uninstalling applications</li>\r\n	<li>Configuring devices and installing device drivers</li>\r\n	<li>Virus and security threats, using antivirus to avoid virus threats