(114, 0, 1, '', '/uploads/courses/1494406860.png', 'CCNA Training in Nepal', 'CCNA Training in Nepal', 'CISCO CERTIFIED NETWORK ASSOCIATE (CCNA) COURSE IN NEPAL', 'CISCO CERTIFIED NETWORK ASSOCIATE (CCNA) COURSE Training in Nepal', 'CCNA (CISCO) Training in Nepal', 'cisco-certified-network-associate-ccna-course-in-nepal', 'CCNA Training in Nepal - Cisco Certified Network Associate Training', 'ccna training in nepal, cisco training in nepal, cisco certified training in nepal, cisco networking training in nepal', 'Certified network associate training by Cisco gives you full scope to grow as a network engineering professional. Enroll today in this ob oriented training.', '', NULL, NULL, '<h2>CISCO Certified Network Associate (CCNA) Training in Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>CCNA Training Course offers the essential guidance to receive certification on operating Cisco&rsquo;s networking devices. The training aims to make the aspiring network technicians familiar with various Cisco Network equipments and their operational environment. Broadway provides world-class Cisco Certified Network Associate (CCNA) training in Nepal to build a foundation for producing globally competent network engineers, network administrators and network technicians.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>CCNA Training Course Highlights:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Career oriented curriculum targeted for everyone interested</li>\r\n	<li>Courses designed as per the CISCO certification requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Detailed knowledge on Fundamentals of Routing and Networking</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding basic aspects of network security</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with handling CISCO routers and switches</li>\r\n	<li>CCNA Certification Exams</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits of CCNA Training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CISCO certified and experienced professionals as CCNA instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Well equipped training labs</li>\r\n	<li>Career focused CCNA training course</li>\r\n	<li>Mock-up exams before actual certification exams</li>\r\n	<li>Internship and job placement opportunity</li>\r\n	<li>Reasonable and affordable training costs apart from CCNA exam fees</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to regularly interact with Cisco experts</li>\r\n	<li>Career counseling for aspiring Network administrators and technicians</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Syllabus Outline</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Understanding basics of CISCO routers and switches</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration and Verification and Troubleshooting&nbsp; routing operation on CISCO devices</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding IP addressing and IP services as per specific network requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Implementation of basic Wide Area Network and Local Area Network</li>\r\n	<li>Identifying network security threats and ways to mitigate them</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Understanding implementation of Network Address translation and Access Control Lists</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a growing demand of Network professionals today as networking projects are increasing worldwide. Acquiring CCNA certification is the starting point of career development in networking. Broadway welcomes all the aspiring Networking engineers and professionals to pursue CCNA training at one of Nepal&rsquo;s finest IT training institutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please contact us via inquiry forms, our social media pages or directly reach visit our office location to reserve your seat for the upcoming CCNA training session at Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '', '1.5 Months', '', '', '', '<h1>CISCO CERTIFIED NETWORK ASSOCIATE (CCNA) COURSE.</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Cisco training course is a dynamic IT certification for <a href=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/hardware/hardware-networking-training-in-nepal\" target=\"_blank\">network training</a> with hands on learning modules to excel career.</p>\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"CCNA Training\" src=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/uploads/courses/CCNA-Training.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" />\r\n', 'Network Engineer', NULL, 73, '2017-06-12 11:29:11', 1),
(115, 0, 1, '', '/uploads/courses/1495964014.png', 'CCNP Training in Nepal', '', 'Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) Course Training', 'Cisco Certified Network Professional (CCNP) Course Training', '', 'cisco-certified-network-professional-ccnp-course', 'CCNP Training in Nepal | Cisco Certified Network Certification Training in Nepal', 'ccnp training in nepal, cisco certified training in nepal, cisco certification in nepal, cisco training in nepal', 'Cisco certified network professional (CCNP) training at gives you full scope to grow as a network engineering professional. Enroll today in this job oriented training.', '', NULL, NULL, '<h2>CCNP Training in Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This training is focused on grooming the passionate network professionals to transform them into a globally competent Cisco certified network technicians. The trainees acquire certification on Cisco networking systems after successful completion of course and certification exam. Broadway provides world class CCNP training in Nepal to inspire the aspiring network professionals to smartly plan, execute, verify and troubleshoot the Wide Area Networks (WANS) and Local Area Network (LANs) at enterprise level.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Course Highlights:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deeper knowledge of Cisco router and switches</li>\r\n	<li>Full coverage of routing and switching in Cisco environment</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding design and implementation of physical as well as virtualized networks</li>\r\n	<li>Understand Systematic Approach to Troubleshooting and maintenance of IP networks</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with network security</li>\r\n	<li>Learning enterprise-level networking roles</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Benefits of CCNP training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Courses designed as per industrial standards and practices</li>\r\n	<li>Cisco certified network experts as instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Well equipped training lab with necessary Cisco networking devices</li>\r\n	<li>Participative and interactive learning environment</li>\r\n	<li>Practical classes to understand complex network solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Facilitation and guidance for certification exams</li>\r\n	<li>Internship and placement opportunities for deserving students</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Syllabus Outline</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Introduction to Router and Routing Protocols</li>\r\n	<li>Implementation and configuration of Cisco IP routing</li>\r\n	<li>Design, implement, validate and troubleshoot WAN and LAN</li>\r\n	<li>Router and Switch Commands</li>\r\n	<li>Implementation of High Availability</li>\r\n	<li>Route Redistribution Concepts and Processes and so on</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>To pursue CCNP training one should have good knowledge of Cisco networking environment as this course provides elaborative concepts on Cisco routers and switches. You can directly contact our inquiry team by filling up inquiry forms or simply sending message on our Facebook page to secure seats for upcoming CCNP training session.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '', '3 Months', '', '', '', '<h3>CISCO CERTIFIED NETWORK PROFESSIONAL (CCNP) COURSE TRAINING COURSE.</h3>\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"CCNP Training in Nepal\" src=\"https://broadwayinfosys.com/uploads/courses/CCNP-Training.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" />\r\n', 'Network Engineer ', NULL, 87, '2017-06-13 09:35:45', 1),
(116, 0, 1, '', '/uploads/courses/1496335513.jpg', 'GIS training in Nepal', 'GIS training in Nepal', 'GIS Training', 'GIS Training in Nepal', 'Geographical Information System Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'gis-training-in-nepal', 'GIS Training in Nepal | Geographical Information System (GIS) Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'gis training in nepal, geographical information system training in nepal, gis institute in nepal, gis courses in nepal', 'Broadway Infosys Nepal offers career-oriented GIS training in Nepal to produce capable and competent GIS experts. Practical learning on geographical information system.', '', NULL, NULL, '<h2><strong>GIS Training in Nepal</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Considering the wider scope of geographic information system skills Broadway offers career-oriented GIS training in Nepal to produce capable and competent GIS experts. The training course covers knowledge on handling specific GIS software to develop analytical maps and analyze spatial data in making quality decision. Civil engineers, surveyors, geographic data enthusiasts, researchers and students are the main target audience for GIS training in Nepal.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Course Highlights</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Learn the foundational concepts of GIS</li>\r\n	<li>Installation of GIS software</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with geospatial concepts and terminologies</li>\r\n	<li>Development of analytical maps</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding spatial analysis techniques</li>\r\n	<li>Mapping of 2D and 3D data</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding implications of GIS knowledge in real world scenario</li>\r\n	<li>Project Work on GIS related topics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Benefits of GIS Training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Professional GIS experts as instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Self-sufficient training lab</li>\r\n	<li>Modern and interactive learning approach</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to get involved in GIS community</li>\r\n	<li>Network building with GIS experts and fellow trainees</li>\r\n	<li>Regular assignments to test GIS knowledge status</li>\r\n	<li>Internship and job placement opportunity at GIS focused organizations</li>\r\n	<li>Customized GIS training course also available for needy students</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '<p>As the number of trainees pursuing GIS course is increasing significantly we would like to recommend you to approach office at the earliest. You can book your seats for the upcoming GIS training by contacting our office or leaving message on our inquiry forms or social media page. We look forward to welcoming you at Broadway Infosys Nepal</p>\r\n', '1 Month ', '', '', '', '<h3>GIS Training</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Introduction to GIS &amp;Installing ArcGIS 10.0</li>\r\n	<li>Working in ArcMap Window, Understanding Toolbars and Menus</li>\r\n	<li>Working with layers</li>\r\n	<li>Selecting Features, Exporting selections</li>\r\n	<li>Using Arc Toolbox (Clip, Dissolve, Merge etc)</li>\r\n	<li>Working with Attributes, Creating and Updating New Attributes</li>\r\n	<li>Using Field Calculator</li>\r\n	<li>Using Symbology</li>\r\n	<li>Creating Layouts, Exporting maps.</li>\r\n	<li>Creating Graphs and Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinate systems</li>\r\n	<li>Projection and Transformation</li>\r\n	<li>Working with Google Earth, Exporting Google Earth data to ArcGIS</li>\r\n	<li>Manual Editing and Editors tool in ArcGIS</li>\r\n	<li>Exporting Excel sheets to ArcGIS</li>\r\n	<li>Managing datasets in Projects</li>\r\n	<li>Georeferencing and Spatial adjustments</li>\r\n	<li>Working with Watershed Tools</li>\r\n	<li>Working with Isoclines (isohyets and contours)</li>\r\n	<li>Generating Raster Datasets</li>\r\n	<li>Geostatistical Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Using GPS, survey techniques</li>\r\n	<li>Map Generation</li>\r\n	<li>Project Work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'GIS Analyst', NULL, 88, '2017-06-06 08:58:00', 1),
(117, 15, 1, 'devicon-photoshop-plain', NULL, '', '', 'Photoshop Training in Nepal', 'Photoshop Training in Nepal', 'Photoshop Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'photoshop-training-in-nepal', 'Photoshop Training in Nepal | Photoshop Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'photoshop training in nepal, photoshop training in kathmandu, photoshop graphic training in nepal', 'Broadway Infosys Offers high quality Adobe Photoshop training, an integral learning to become a graphic design professional. Enroll today.', '', NULL, NULL, '<h2><strong>Adobe Photoshop Training in Nepal</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This training prepares the aspiring designers to handle various Adobe products for performing specific tasks such as creating logos, flyers, digital magazines, designing web pages etc. Broadway offers career-oriented Adobe Photoshop training in Nepal to produce professionally competitive web and graphics designers. Also, the training is equally important for video professionals, brand executives, media executives and any individual interested to learn Photoshop.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Course Highlights</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Understand fundamental concepts of Photoshop</li>\r\n	<li>Learning implications of Adobe Photoshop in real world scenario</li>\r\n	<li>Learn to create, modify and enhance images</li>\r\n	<li>Learning techniques &nbsp;to create banners, website mockups and design interfaces</li>\r\n	<li>Learn to design web templates, brochures, newsletters etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Project Work under supervision of instructors and experts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Benefits of Adobe Photoshop Training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experienced and Adobe certified professionals as instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Career oriented Adobe Photoshop training course</li>\r\n	<li>Regular assignments to test Photoshop skills</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to expand professional network with web and graphics designers</li>\r\n	<li>Internship and job 