(10, 'Amrit Karki', 'amritkarki25@gmail.com', '9849781278', '9802920938', 'AutoCAD', '', '/uploads/instructor/1491144003.pdf', 'Dear sir/ma\'am,\r\nI am writing to apply for the position of AutoCAD instructor.\r\nI am currently a Master’s candidate at the Institute of Engineering, Thapathali Campus in Mechanical Systems Design and Engineering and fully expect to complete my Master’s degree requirements by 2019.\r\nHaving recently obtained my Bachelor’s Degree in Mechanical Engineering from TU-IOE Pashchimanchal campus (WRC), I wish to bring my knowledge, skills and commitment to your college’s learning environment.\r\nAfter my graduation, I have been fortunate enough to serve as a tutor in Vector Group Pvt. Ltd. Through my participation as a tutor, I have developed confidence and an interest in teaching and look forward to the opportunity to teach assigned classes.\r\nI am enclosing my Curriculum Vitae. If you require any additional materials or information, I am happy to supply it. Thank you very much for your consideration.\r\nSincerely,\r\nAmrit Karki', '2017-04-02 08:55:03', '2017-04-02 08:55:03'),
