(17, 'Nirajan Rijal', 'nirajanrijal2007@yahoo.com', '4157679120', '4157679120', 'Data Analysis, Project Management ', '', '/uploads/instructor/1495498984.docx', 'I am in USA now, Coming to Nepal on May 31th , Bachelor in Finance From KU, Nepal. Master in Information Assurance From Saint Cloud State University, USA. And Have Few Microsoft certificate and will be more certificate in data analyst in Future. ', '2017-05-22 18:38:05', '2017-05-22 18:38:05'),
(18, 'Sandip kumar Nepal', 'sandip.nepal40@gmail.com', '9582579143', '', 'Core Java, Advance Java, Hibernate, Spring', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandip-kumar-nepal-311156121/', '/uploads/instructor/1495513614.docx', 'I have a good experience of teaching Java. Also I have six months of experience in an IT Company, as well as three years of freelancing experience. I consider myself suitable as a Java Developer as well as a Java Trainer.', '2017-05-22 22:41:54', '2017-05-22 22:41:54'),
(19, 'Subash Ghimire', 'sghimire47@gmail.com', '9841193424', '', 'Joomla,Magento,Shopify,BigCommerce,WordPress,OpenCart,CI', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/subash-ghimire/', '/uploads/instructor/1495604607.pdf', 'I am a passionate and energetic person and anything about the web technology interests me. That is the reason why, I have been working as a PHP Web Developer. My objective is to keep myself updated and specialize in building web application with the latest technologies.', '2017-05-23 23:58:27', '2017-05-23 23:58:27'),
(20, 'Gaurav Jayasawal', 'jgaurav6@gmail.com', '9971847753', '9971847753', 'Android Development', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/gaurav-jayasawal', '/uploads/instructor/1495664670.docx', 'I am an energetic, hard working Android application developer with the skills to execute projects individually as well as in a group keeping deadlines and quality of work as a priority.', '2017-05-24 16:39:30', '2017-05-24 16:39:30'),
(21, 'Sandeep Kumar Bist', 'sbist17@gmail.com', '9864994394', '', 'Java', '', '/uploads/instructor/1497919902.docx', 'Sandeep Kumar Bist\r\n\r\nPatan-6 Baitadi, Nepal\r\n9864994394\r\nsbist17@gmail.com\r\n\r\nBroadway Infosys\r\nKathmandu \r\n\r\nDear HR Manager,\r\nThis letter is to express my keen interest in becoming Java Instructor. To switch my career from Mechanical Engineer to Java Developer, I went through an intense training on Complete Java for 1.5 years. With the theoretical and pragmatic skills I fostered on Java technologies like Spring, Hibernate, Web Services Applications and Hadoop; I feel confident to work on java based diverse projects (standalone, web, enterprise as well as distributed applications) and certain to be valuable asset to your organization. \r\n\r\nAs a follower of the “STAY HUNGRY STAY FOOLISH” principle, I love being challenged and sticking to projects that require an assiduous work beyond my comfort and knowledge set, as continuing to learn new languages and development techniques are important to me and the success of your organization.\r\n\r\nYour listed requirements closely match my background and skills. A few I would like to highlight that would enable me to contribute to your bottom line are:\r\n•	Having exposure in Design and Development of Distributed and Client-Server applications using Object Oriented Analysis, Design with JAVA (OOPs, Multithreading, Exception Handling, Generics, Collections, Regular Expression, Serialization, File IO), and J2EE Technologies.\r\n•	Expertise with J2EE Technologies (Servlets, JSP, JSTL, JDBC, JNDI).\r\n•	Expertise in implementing MVC architecture usingJ2EE and J2SE design patterns.\r\n•	Having good knowledge of ORM tool such as Hibernate and JPA.\r\n•	Having expertise knowledge in spring framework (Spring Core Container, Spring Web, Spring Data Access/Integration and Transactions, and Aspect Oriented Programming) along with Hibernate.\r\n•	Knowledge of Web Services client generation and process of XML using JAX-WS, JAXB, JAXP, SOAP, WSDL, and Restful Services.\r\n•	Thorough knowledge of XML technologies (DOM, SAX parsers), and extensive experience with XML schema, DTD’s, XSD.\r\n•	Thorough knowledge of Hadoop (HDFS, Map Reduce, Pig, Hive, Hbase, Flume, Scoop).\r\n•	Thorough knowledge of web-technologies like HTML, CSS and JavaScript.\r\n•	Thorough knowledge of core design patterns and J2EE design patterns like Singleton, Factory Design, Business Delegate, Model View Controller (MVC), Data Access Object, Front Controller, Service Locator, Decorator Design, Pagination, Fly Weight Design, Command Design, Proxy Design, Template Method, Adapter Design, Inversion of Control (IOC) and Value Object\r\n•	Basic Knowledge on JMS Application, Spring Boot, Swagger API.\r\n•	Good exposure in working with Database Oracle and MYSQL.\r\n•	Handful of experience in developing applications using IDE’s like Eclipse, Sts, Jdeveloper.\r\n•	Experience in Application Servers like Weblogic Server, JBOSS and Apache Tomcat, Wildfly10.\r\n•	Excellent communication, interpersonal and analytical skills and highly motivated team player with the ability to work independently.\r\n•	Ability to learn and adapt quickly to the emerging new technologies and paradigms\r\n\r\n\r\nI’ve attached a copy of my resume that details my projects and experience in web app  and desktop app development. I can be reached anytime via my cell phone, 9864994394 or via email at sbist17@gmail.com.\r\nThank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to speaking with you in person about this opportunity.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nSandeep K Bist\r\n', '2017-06-19 19:06:42', '2017-06-19 19:06:42'),
(22, 'Manjul Bhattarai', 'manjul.atern@gmail.com', '9860670237', '9860670237', 'Java, PHP, Web Technology, Python', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/manjul-bhattarai-ba296187/', '/uploads/instructor/1497943357.docx', 'Hello,\r\n\r\nI am a software developer currently working in Logpoint Solutions Pvt. Ltd. I am also currently giving my lectures on Java, Spring MVC, and React JS to the students of Nepal College of Information Technology which they learn as elective subjects. I generally take lectures at NCIT on saturday and sunday and i have leisure time on morning time of the weekdays (Monday-Friday). I am looking for a part time job to share my knowledge to the students so that they can start their professional career.', '2017-06-20 01:37:37', '2017-06-20 01:37:37'),
(23, 'Sagun Karanjit', 'karanjit.sagun01@gmail.com', '9849183423', '', 'C# .Net ', '', '/uploads/instructor/1498026097.pdf', 'I have studied Computer Engineering from Advanced College of Engineering and Management and passed out with sound results. I have good communication skills and have experience in teaching as a lab assistant as well as have taught primary level students. To this date, I have 1 and half year of experience in c# technologies and additionally, I have worked in web platform and java.', '2017-06-21 00:36:37', '2017-06-21 00:36:37'),
