(26, 'Pratik Gautam', 'gautamxpratik@gmail.com', '9803683285', '9803683285', 'Python, Django, JavaScript, jQuery, React, PostgreSQL, PostGIS, Web/GIS Development', 'www.linkedin.com/in/pratik-gautam', '/uploads/instructor/1498453318.pdf', 'Web/GIS developer with over 3 years of professional experience in cloud and web based full stack GIS software development in Python (Python 3, Django), JavaScript (jQuery, React) PostgreSQL (PostGIS). Team player with the initiative to foster knowledge sharing and collective problem solving.', '2017-06-25 23:16:58', '2017-06-25 23:16:58'),
