(1, '1', 1, 'About Us', 'About Us', 'about-us', NULL, 'About Us <br>', '', 'About Us', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the best inclusive computer training institutes in Kathmandu, Nepal. Established in 2008, our professional IT Training and Development center has been employing experts in this field to impart professional education to trainees. We offer well-structured complete professional training in various programming languages, graphics &amp; multimedia, web designing as well as development and hardware, networking training that is based upon the current recruitment needs in the IT market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To summarize, Broadway Infosys is a complete learning institute that not only provides training on various IT courses but also prepares students to smartly handle the real working environment. We are dedicated and committed towards:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Providing quality IT training to the aspiring IT professionals</li>\r\n	<li>Availability of highly qualified and experienced instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Assigning project works as per the nature of the courses</li>\r\n	<li>Conducting regular project work evaluation sessions</li>\r\n	<li>Identifying trainees&rsquo; skills and knowledge gaps</li>\r\n	<li>Taking corrective actions to enhance trainees&rsquo; skills</li>\r\n	<li>Providing internship and job placement facilities to the trainees</li>\r\n	<li>Building long-term trustful relationship with the trainees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Since establishment, we have successfully established and maintained network with more than fifty IT and other companies which has made us able to offer and provide our students with internship and job opportunities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Vision</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;To empower the nation through generation of computer literates and competent IT professionals who could serve as valuable resource and responsible innovative citizens.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Mission</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Broadway Infosys Nepal&#39;s team is and will be dedicated to develop and impart quality IT training and service to all; achieving excellence in creative, innovative and up to-date teaching-learning, facilitating effective interactions among faculty, management and students and acting as a contributing institution for the employees, society and all stakeholders.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Core Values</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Broadway Infosys believes in fundamental values that are aimed at serving our valuable stakeholders with quality services. We have developed following set of core values that is directed towards our vision:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>People:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We attract and train the great minds</li>\r\n	<li>Our trainees are our greatest focus</li>\r\n	<li>We treat each other with respect and dignity</li>\r\n	<li>We are always committed towards producing satisfied trainees</li>\r\n	<li>Build long-term relationship with all the trainees, instructors and other stakeholders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ethics:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Maintain the highest ethical standards with trainees, instructors, communities and all other stakeholders</li>\r\n	<li>Be accountable to our services and ethical practices</li>\r\n	<li>We always encourage honest feedback and suggestions regarding our services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Trust:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We are determined to serve the stakeholders on what matters the most</li>\r\n	<li>We have a consistent desire to improve the quality of training and win the market</li>\r\n	<li>We promote transparency in our services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Leadership:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We have a well-defined vision that is effectively communicated to our trainees, instructors and all the stakeholders</li>\r\n	<li>We don&#39;t hesitate to take risks and lead from the front in pressing situations</li>\r\n	<li>We believe in producing leaders rather than followers</li>\r\n	<li>We believe IT skills coupled with leadership qualities produce an unbeatable IT professional</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Social Responsibility:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We believe sense of social responsibility adds value to any business</li>\r\n	<li>We are proactive in helping the society during crisis situations</li>\r\n	<li>We make sure our trainees also become a socially responsible individual</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Broadway&#39;s Objectives</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our core objective is to train people who are keen to start professional IT career and learn job related skills in order to turn them into effective and efficient IT professionals who will then be using computing technology to develop effective information systems for solving real life problems in diverse organizational environments.<br />\r\nTherefore, we are committed and dedicated towards achieving the following objectives:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To impart value-based IT knowledge and skills</li>\r\n	<li>To create employment in IT sector</li>\r\n	<li>To bridge the gap between skilled manpower and aspiring IT companies</li>\r\n	<li>To act as a platform for grooming one&#39;s IT skill</li>\r\n	<li>To promote startup culture in Nepal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why Broadway Infosys Nepal?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>While we are celebrating nine glorious years of success at Broadway Infosys here are as many reasons why you should come to this wonderland that will change yourself for the rest of your lives</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We put more emphasis in providing <strong>effective career counselling </strong>understanding the training needs of the aspiring IT individuals.</li>\r\n	<li>We have a pool of <strong>qualified and experienced instructors</strong> who bring the remarkable blend of knowledge and experience to the delight of every trainee. A Broadway trainer always means a smart, outspoken, innovative and a passionate team player with years of experience working with local and global IT community.</li>\r\n	<li>We offer <strong>time, skill and competency based courses </strong>for the trainees with specific areas of interest and proficiency and design the training curriculum as per your demand and necessity.</li>\r\n	<li>We have <strong>course wise training materials</strong> so that trainees get the required resources as per particular training curriculum.</li>\r\n	<li>Our infrastructure consist of <strong>well-equipped computer labs, comfortable seating arrangements and other necessary etiquettes</strong> constituting a full-fledged training institute.</li>\r\n	<li>We offer <strong>regular, fast track and weekend courses</strong> along with live <strong>online/virtual</strong> training and <strong>accommodation service with hostel facility</strong> understanding our trainees&rsquo; requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>We serve as an <strong>exciting platform to meet and network</strong> with the experts, innovators, employers and the business players who closely work with you to explore and experiment the emerging talents that are groomed here at Broadway.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; So, come as a stranger, learn in a team and leave with a network.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We facilitate <strong>hands on learning experience</strong> with encouragement for interactive classes, project development and guidance along with required <strong>soft skill learning</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>We have established a <strong>regular interactive training evaluation culture</strong> in our institute by encouraging the trainees to honestly present their feedback, suggestions and healthy criticisms to any training curriculum, resources and environment.</li>\r\n	<li>We ensure<strong> 100 % guarantee of internship and job placement</strong> for outstanding learners at Broadway Infosys and other organizations within our network.</li>\r\n	<li>We build <strong>long term trust based relationship</strong> with our trainees.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Benefits of Job-oriented IT training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To summarize the key reasons to join Broadway Infosys here are the 10 benefits of Job-oriented IT training in Nepal that pave the &quot;highway&quot; for the trainees to reach the career destination the way Broadway does:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Learning and Earning</li>\r\n	<li>Getting enhanced competitiveness of IT professionals</li>\r\n	<li>Learning smart work rather than hard work</li>\r\n	<li>Regular feedback and improvement inputs</li>\r\n	<li>Learning Courses designed as per the job market needs</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding that you don&rsquo;t need to be a &ldquo;techie&rdquo; to learn software skills</li>\r\n	<li>Learning only what is important</li>\r\n	<li>Networking with the industry professionals and experts</li>\r\n	<li>Becoming the &ldquo;most wanted talent&rdquo; IT companies seek</li>\r\n	<li>Enhancing your soft skills polishing yourself to be ready to work.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Broadway Quality Training Approach</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At Broadway Infosys, we work understanding the very concept of &ldquo;training&rdquo;,i.e bringing a person to an agreed standard of proficiency by practice and instruction.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We first ensure and then access.</li>\r\n	<li>We thrive to identify proper training needs of trainees.</li>\r\n	<li>We carry out continuous resources assessment, competences&#39; assessment and IT market analysis.</li>\r\n	<li>We implement practical project based learning approach by continuously updating training courses.</li>\r\n	<li>We believe in providing supportive teaching- learning materials/resources.</li>\r\n	<li>We practice effective communication between faculty, students and management.</li>\r\n	<li>We carry out continuous training evaluation at regular intervals and pay sincere attention to the feedback, both positive and negative.</li>\r\n	<li>We believe in maintaining cooperative learning environment with discipline and Broadway corporate values.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;We insist in continuous interactivity throughout training sessions.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;We focus on trainees&rsquo; overall performance adopting vocational training approach</li>\r\n	<li>We are committed to prepare trainees in technical as well as personality and behavioral dimensions</li>\r\n	<li>We specially focus on the overall performance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Broadway Events:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>-We organize</p>\r\n\r\n<p>regular workshops, brainstorming sessions, focus group discussions, guest lectures and talk programs with the industry experts, professionals, critics, media, private business houses and government officials to identify and analyze the existing problems and opportunities in IT sector</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-We participate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>in events and exhibitions like CAN Infotech, CAN Comtech in order to introduce our services and at the same time create IT awareness satisfying queries of interested students in their desired courses and client&rsquo;s interest in development services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-We collaborate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>with IT and Engineering colleges and universities by sponsoring in different technology related programs encouraging the students to exhibit their creativeness and knowledge and accumulate self-confidence in the same. To take an instance sponsorship in LITE exhibition organized by Kantipur Engineering College.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-We cooperate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>with different colleges, universities and corporate organizations by facilitating training instructors in their respective premises to provide training to the interested students in the place itself. Recent examples could be IT training in &ldquo;Himalayan White House College&rdquo;,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-We encourage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IT creative individuals to demonstrate their project to the IT sector professional and act as a bridge to enable way for the fresh IT graduates to meet their prospective employers by organizing interview sessions in consented premises.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Further,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>we organize various social events like cleaning campaign, scholarship distribution, free IT trainings to financially incapable students, top students relief tour to the villages struggling from natural disaster and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We wholeheartedly encourage our trainees to participate in social activities and gain real life experience in project management, human resource mobilization, communication skills and other essential management skills in a realistic and a fun way.</p>\r\n', 'About us | Broadway Infosys - #1 Computer Training Institute in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'about us, about broadway infosys nepal', 'Broadway Infosys Nepal, established in 2008 is Nepal\'s oldest and the most comprehensive IT & computer training institute. It offers more than 83 computer courses with most affordable price range.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 03:51:06', '2017-03-23 09:57:34', 1),
(2, '2', 0, 'Our Services', 'Our Services', 'our-services', NULL, 'Our Services', '', '', '', '<h2>Web and Software Development Training</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide extensive training on web development and software development for the aspiring developers. Our web and software development training is focused on acquainting trainees with modern practices of website development, web applications development and software development that are quality oriented and cost-effective. We understand the greater career scope for software developers worldwide and considering this fact we have designed special web development and software development training courses that address the existing and potential market needs of software industry. Our highly qualified and experienced instructors have been regularly interacting with various IT (software) companies to understand the emerging trends in software development. Understanding and analyzing the real market scenario we are continuously producing smart web developers and software developers from our focused training programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Apps Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Considering the wider usage of smartphones and increasing popularity of mobile applications we have established apps development wing that has specialized in mobile apps development for Android devices, iPhones, iPads, Windows platform etc. We provide research-based apps development service to the companies from multiple sectors prioritizing and guaranteeing genuine return on investment. Our mobile apps development wing is represented by highly qualified and experienced team of mobile application developers that are familiar to the emerging trends in apps development. Further, we also provide extensive training on mobile apps development for various popular platforms such as Android, iOS and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Software Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide software development services to every type of businesses that seek to improve their operational efficiency through implementation of software technologies. Our software development services comprise of simple application development to enterprise level applications development. The experienced developers with adequate expertise in software development have been our valuable assets for delivering the software projects as per clients&rsquo; expectations and maintaining excellent support service. With the expertise and commitment of experienced designers, developers, quality assurance engineers we make sure the right project activities are carried out in specific stages of software development life cycle. Our portfolio proves that we care about not only the software needs of the businesses but also the economic value the software guarantees for any business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Web Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our expertise in web development has been reflected by the experienced web team and the portfolio it has developed till date. We provide focused web development services to the businesses that wish for impactful online presence to stay ahead of the competition. Our web development team comprising of website analysts, UX /UI designers, developers, Search Engine Optimization experts makes sure the clients generate good return on their website investment by attracting significant number of their customers online. The client testimonials and quality training on web design and development that we provide are the reflections of degree of excellence of our web development team. Should you be looking to invest on your company&rsquo;s web presence we are happy to serve you with excellence.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Web Hosting</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It is often problematic for companies to find a reliable hosting service provider to prevent loss of revenue, malware attacks on websites and unfavorable impacts on SEO rankings. We provide special hosting services to the companies as per the nature of their business and significance of online presence. We understand the scalability aspect of any business website and have therefore designed special hosting packages to facilitate smooth functioning of website even during high traffic and data loading. You should remember that choosing a right web hosting partner could be your most crucial business decision as many businesses have suffered significantly making a bad choice of hosting service provider.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Domain Registration</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We also provide domain registration service to the individuals, companies and all kinds of businesses. We love to help individuals and companies seeking entry into the world of web by suggesting effective domain names that relate to their business profile. As we believe the good domain names help in effective branding, attracting website visitors and credibility enhancement of companies, our domain registration service comprises of full domain registration cycle from general business analysis, finding effective domain names to hassle free domain registration.</p>\r\n', 'Our Services - Web & Apps Development, Software Development, Web Hosting', 'it services in nepal, web development in nepal, apps development in nepal, software development in nepal', 'Broadway Infosys Nepal offers comprehensive IT services including web and apps development, software development, web hosting and domain registration etc.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 07:21:18', '2017-03-23 10:00:59', 1),
(3, '1', 2, 'Careers @ BIN', 'Career', 'career', NULL, 'Career', '', '', '', '', 'Career Opportunities by Broadway Infosys Nepal - Career at BIN', 'career opportunities by Broadway Infosys Nepal, IT career in Nepal', 'Broadway Infosys Nepal offers extensive career opportunities for IT students. Enroll with us & get yourself career rewarding opportunities.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 07:21:24', '2017-05-18 07:58:35', 1),
(4, '1', 4, 'Hostel Facility', 'Broadway Accommodation Service/IT Hostel', 'broadway-accommodation-service', NULL, 'Broadway Accomodation Service/ IT Hostel', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal cares not only about the quality training facilities to the students but also about the basic necessities of students coming to Broadway for pursuing training on various courses. Broadway Infosys has therefore introduced accommodation facilities to the trainees that come from outside Kathmandu valley and foreign countries enabling them to complete their training program with ease and convenience. In this way, the trainees would not have to face any difficulties in accessing lodging facilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Prime Location</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Broadway Infosys Nepal premise is located in Tinkune, Subhidanagar, which is a prime location near to International Airport. Focusing on our trainees &lsquo;requirement, convenience and easy accessibility with no need of any travel expenses, we have facilitated our hostel location just 5 minutes walking distance from our training center . We also have tie-up with affordable hotels and lodges located near our center providing sufficient alternatives for our trainees to opt the most suited one for them to stay and learn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have already provided the accommodation service to the students visiting from<strong> Biratnagar, Birgunj, Chitwan, Janakpur, Saptari, Siraha, Pokhara, Bhairawa, Dhading </strong>and international students from <strong>Bhutan, India, South Africa, Canada, U.K, Australia </strong>and<strong> U.S.A.</strong> And their feedback in their experience regarding accommodation in our hostel and lodge has given us confidence to assure you for getting reasonable and convenient stay throughout the learning period.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: If you opt to stay in some other hotels apart from our hostel or preferred lodges, we can provide adequate help and support in locating appropriate hotels nearby our training center as we have mentioned above that our training center is in prime location with maximum number of hotels and lodges available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our associates will be available to pick you up directly from the airport and take you to our hostel and other hotels to know your preference and then you will soon start your journey of broad learning experience!!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Accommodation/Food</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our hostel comprises of facility of either both food and accommodation or only accommodation as per your preference. You can pay a bit higher price for both food and room or pay for your room only in cheaper price and make arrangement for eating somewhere else as per your choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The number, type and nature of rooms or number of trainees in a room both in hostel and hotel will be determined accordingly to your need and suitability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For further details regarding type, number of room, food, price and other features, please feel free to contact our associate at 01-4111849 or mail us at <a href=\"mailto:info@broadwayinfosys.com\">info@broadwayinfosys.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Broadway Broad Learning experience</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Broadway accommodation facility gives you a broad learning experience in the sense that along with comfortable, cheap, clean and convenient stay, you get to experience more concentrated learning.You can learn as scheduled in class, return to hostel/lodge, come back or stay anytime at Broadway hall or any study room throughout the day for practicing in spare time.With availability of trainers and developers, one can also take assistance in their assignments if required.Our high speed internet access and uninterrupted power supply will assist you to focus on your learning throughout your stay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thus, our hostel facilities are being provided to serve the following objectives:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To reflect Broadway&#39;s commitment and dedication to serve the trainees in every possible way</li>\r\n	<li>To save significant amount of time and cost that trainees have to incur in finding convenient lodging facility</li>\r\n	<li>To ensure homely and friendly environment to trainees</li>\r\n	<li>To ensure broad learning with staying experience</li>\r\n	<li>To increase social bonding of trainees coming to Broadway from various parts of the world.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Broadway accomodation - Hostel Facility for IT students in Kathmandu, Nepal', 'it hostel, it students hostel', 'IT hostel by Broadway Infosys Nepal offers accommodation and hostel facility for students.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 07:23:07', '2017-05-18 07:55:55', 1),
(5, '1', 6, '', 'IT Internship and Placement in Nepal. Internship & Placement by Broadway Infosys.', 'internship-placement', NULL, 'IT Internship and Placement in Nepal', 'Internship/Placement by Broadway Infosys', 'INTERNSHIP/PLACEMENT', '', '<p>The internship and placement opportunity facilitated by Broadway Infosys is a wonderful opportunity to test your knowledge, skills and project work experience in real work scenario. Our strong network with more than 50 IT companies in the country serves as the gateway for our trainees to enter into the real-life tech world of exciting opportunities and challenges. The companies having all time rewarding corporate relationship with us regularly screen the trainees and offer them internship and job opportunity on the basis of their core focus, interest and skills. We ensure that every trainee gets a chance to learn from the top players in local as well as global IT business and they become genuinely competitive before starting tech career in their specific field of choice. And remember, the internship programs arranged for our trainees are mostly paid; it&rsquo;s a bonus for you in addition to valuable knowledge, skills and experience you get during the internship period.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Basically, our internship program revolves around the following core objectives:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To groom the technical, interpersonal, and informational skills of the trainees</li>\r\n	<li>To provide enabling environment for trainees to learn the most from experienced mentors</li>\r\n	<li>To make the trainees accustomed with the organizational culture</li>\r\n	<li>To impart professionalism and leadership qualities in trainees</li>\r\n	<li>To make interns understand the basic concept of project life cycle</li>\r\n	<li>To ensure the trainees are better positioned when they start their actual working career</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The aforementioned internship objectives are relevant to the trainees pursuing internship in their desired field of interest just as web application development, multimedia, mobile application development, and portal development and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also categorize the trainees on the basis of level of expertise they have and the internship is planned at respective companies that could best fit their skills and personality. We make sure that our trainees are placed at the companies that could best comply with their career aspirations. Further, the events and project works that we design as per the trainees&rsquo; interests and competencies are very important tools to facilitate internships and job placements for our trainees. We also provide internship opportunity to the developers in Broadway itself helping them to groom their technical, interpersonal, and informational skills. We strongly encourage IT creative individuals to demonstrate their project to the IT professionals and organize interview sessions in consented premises for <strong>job placement</strong>. Many of our alumni have been already working for the reputed companies in the country and our success gallery cites our achievement in this objective.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>So, come as a stranger, learn in a team, leave with a network and explore a bright career with Broadway......!</strong></p>\r\n', 'Internship Placement - Interns Job - Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'internship placement, internship jobs, intern jobs', 'The internship and placement opportunity facilitated by Broadway Infosys is a wonderful opportunity to test your knowledge, skills and project work experience in real work scenario.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 07:25:07', '2017-03-28 08:36:42', 1),
(6, '0', 0, '', 'Welcome Message', 'welome-to-broadway', NULL, 'WELCOME TO BROADWAY INFOSYS NEPAL', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the best inclusive computer training institutes in Kathmandu, Nepal. Established in 2008, our professional IT Training and Development center has been employing experts in this field to impart professional education to trainees. We offer well-structured complete professional training in various Programming Languages, Graphics &amp; Multimedia, Web Designing as well as Development Training that is based upon the current recruitment needs in the IT market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To summarize, Broadway Infosys is a complete learning institute that not only provides training on various IT courses but also prepares students to smartly handle the real working environment. We are dedicated and committed towards:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Providing quality IT training to the aspiring IT professionals</li>\r\n	<li>Availability of highly qualified and experienced instructors</li>\r\n	<li>Assigning project works as per the nature of the courses</li>\r\n	<li>Conducting regular project work evaluation sessions</li>\r\n	<li>Identifying trainees&rsquo; skills and knowledge gaps</li>\r\n	<li>Taking corrective actions to enhance trainees&rsquo; skills</li>\r\n	<li>Providing internship and job placement facilities to the trainees</li>\r\n	<li>Building long-term trustful relationship with the trainees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Since establishment, we have successfully established and maintained network with more than fifty IT and other companies which has made us able to offer and provide our students with internship and job opportunities.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 01:51:09', '2017-03-21 03:02:32', 1),
(7, '4', 5, '', 'Scholarship', 'scholarship', NULL, 'Scholarship', '', 'Scholarship', '', '<p>Scholarship content goes here</p>\r\n', 'Scholarship - IT Training Scholarship - Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'scholarship for it training', 'Scholarship in IT training gives you an opportunity to sharpen your skills. With your talent, you can achieve valued scholarship today.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 22:49:52', '2017-03-28 08:39:57', 1),
(8, '0', 0, '', 'Help & Faq', 'help-faq', NULL, 'Help and FAQ', '', '', '', '<p>help and faq goes here</p>\r\n', 'FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions - Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'faq, frequently asked questions', 'Frequently asked questions - Broadway Infosys Nepal. If you couldn\'t find your answer, you can contact us at info@broadwayinfosys.com', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 22:50:40', '2017-03-28 09:23:49', 1),
(9, '4', 0, '', 'Online Training', 'online-training', NULL, 'Online Training', '', 'Online Training', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While the world is largely relying on technologies for almost everything we have also been adopting online (web-based) IT training practices to serve the aspiring developers/programmers and professionals from around the globe. We understand the significance of virtual training setting that is focused on assisting individuals who have busy schedule or are at distant places. Since last eight years we have been providing virtual training to the students that are unable to visit our physical classroom location or are dispersed over the various parts of the world. The trainees from around the world have been benefitted significantly in enhancing their technical skills via our specially designed online training courses. Currently, our online training courses include Web Designing, PHP, Java, .NET, Wordpress, Android etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why you should pursue Online Training Courses?.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Even though if you are not comfortable with your time schedule or distance to take our training classes at our physical location, it does not make any difference as you will learn everything you require joining our online training course of your choice. You should pursue online training courses at</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Broadway Infosys for the following key reasons:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Convenient for the students that are interested in our courses but are at distant locations</li>\r\n	<li>Higher level of comfort and concentration for trainees pursuing online courses from their convenient locations</li>\r\n	<li>Cost-effective and time saving training packages</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced Instructors with years of online training expertise</li>\r\n	<li>Hundreds of students from around the world have already completed online training courses</li>\r\n	<li>Customized training methodologies as part of special consideration for online trainees</li>\r\n	<li>Equal placement opportunity for the deserving students that pursue online training</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to engage yourself in teamwork with trainees from different parts of the world</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Online Training is primarily targeted for the individuals who are:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Outside Nepal or within Nepal but unable to visit our physical location</li>\r\n	<li>Interested in our training courses but are working full-time</li>\r\n	<li>Comfortable with their own physical setting</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate about relying on technologies for everything</li>\r\n	<li>Hesitant or feel monotonous and boring to travel same location everyday</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'Online IT Training - Virtual Training - Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'online it training, online training, online computer training, online it courses', 'Since last eight years we have been providing virtual training to the students that are unable to visit our physical classroom location or are dispersed over the various parts of the world.', '', '/uploads/pages/1492620342.jpg', '', '', '2016-10-26 23:13:10', '2017-04-19 11:00:42', 1),
(10, '0', 0, '', 'Training', 'training', NULL, '', '', 'Training', '', '<h1>Training in Nepal. Computer Training in Nepal</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The training at Broadway Infosys Nepal is always a wise investment decision for aspiring IT professionals seeking successful career in global technology industry. The adequate training resources, qualified and experienced instructors, friendly learning environment and exciting post-training opportunities have uniquely positioned Broadway in Nepalese IT training industry. We offer a wide range of IT training courses that have been designed as per the latest technological trends and recruitment needs of the global competitive job market.We provide extensive training on web development, software development, programming along with hardware, and networking addressing the existing and potential market needs of IT industry. Our web, software and hardware development training is focused on acquainting trainees with modern practices of website development, web applications development, software development and hardware networking that are quality oriented and cost-effective. Our training sessions consist of:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-Individual</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Addressing the needs of trainees, individual training classes are also organized where the trainee can study alone with the course instructor at agreeable training fees. Usually, this training session characterizes fast track courses where trainee need to complete courses before the exact duration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-Group</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We offer regular training sessions with maximum 10 students in a group as per the interested course making it easy and convenient for the trainees and the trainer to study more effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>-Corporate</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also provide corporate training facility to the corporate organizations who require training to be provided in mass for the particular level of employees in any required course. The training can be both in-house and off-house. If required, we can also facilitate our instructors to the corporate premises for the training.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Modes of Training Delivery</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>i.<strong> Classroom/ On- location</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Broadway Infosys, you experience warm, friendly and supportive learning environment with well-managed infrastructure and technology suiting your training needs. The Broadway team is always committed to provide utmost satisfaction to the trainees while providing classroom, on-location training within Broadway premises. When needed, we have enough halls and labs to facilitate the trainees to utilize their leisure time in practicing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All the labs and halls are well-facilitated with high speed dedicated internet access with uninterrupted 24 hour power supply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ii. <strong>Live Virtual /Online</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With our Live Online training courses, we have been able to provide similar learning experience as our on location classroom based courses. With growing demand, use and objective to meet the requirements of our out of valley and international students, we decided to initiate live online training and have been successfully providing the service since four years. With the inception of Broadway Infosys USA in United States of America, our online training trend has increased with greater extent. With live online courses, you directly learn from and interact with a live expert instructor from your convenient location and can get to involve in discussions, practice, assignments and get to know your progress throughout the course.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 23:17:30', '2017-03-23 01:05:46', 1),
(11, '1', 3, 'Upload Your Resume', 'Upload Resume', 'resume/upload', NULL, 'Upload Your Resume', '', NULL, NULL, '<p>Broadway offers round the year employment &amp; job opportunities to the aspiring and experienced working professionals. If you&rsquo;re looking for an opportunity to join the promising and exciting team of Broadway or any other wonderful companies among our collaborating partners we would love to hear from you at the earliest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your resume would be the best way to get started &ndash; all you need to do is fill up the form at the right and upload your latest resume- and leave the rest to us. We would love to hear directly from you should you be interested to contact us in person.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-27 00:00:47', '2017-03-10 07:18:51', 1),
(12, '1', 1, 'Contact Us', 'Contact Us', 'contact-us', NULL, 'Contact Us', '', '', '', '', 'Contact Us - Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'contact broadway infosys nepal, how to contact broadway infosys nepal, contact number broadway infosys nepal', 'Contact Broadway Infosys Nepal. Our phone numbers are - +977-01-4117578 & 4111849. Our email address is: info@broadwayinfosysnepal.com.', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-27 05:58:02', '2017-03-23 10:25:13', 1),
(13, '0', 6, 'Evaluation', 'Evaluation', 'evaluation', NULL, 'Evaluation', 'IT Project Work Evaluation', 'Evaluation', '', '<p>The evaluation of project work is carried out by our qualified and experienced team of instructors and industry experts to explore and identify the talent, skills and creativity of trainees. The evaluation process involves thorough analysis and measurement of trainees&rsquo; project work performance. The project evaluation remains as one of the influencing factors contributing for trainees&rsquo; opportunity to pursue professional career as intern or full time professionals with leading companies in and outside the country. The highly competitive trainees secure quick job placement while the trainees requiring additional improvement are encouraged to work upon their weaknesses and turn themselves into competitive IT workforce.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-11-15 07:37:53', '2017-03-13 06:23:13', 1),
