(24, '1', 1, '', 'Project Work', 'project-work', NULL, 'Project Work for IT Students', '', 'Project Work', '', '<p>The project work is intended to test the skills, knowledge and other fundamental outcomes of training. The nature of project work depends upon the courses pursued by the trainees. Broadway designs the individual and group project works to encourage trainees to apply the important knowledge acquired from the training in real life scenario. The trending technologies, business significance of various applications and trainees&rsquo; passion, competence and important skills are considered while designing project works at Broadway. We conduct project works at the end of every training session when the trainees have received the required theoretical and practical knowledge.</p>\r\n', 'IT Project Work at Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'IT project work', 'Broadway Infosys Nepal offers project work along with your IT course. Get ahead with professional project work and practical learning.', '', NULL, '', '', '2017-03-08 11:45:37', '2017-05-18 08:00:48', 1),
