(29, '0', 0, '', 'Domain Registration', 'services/domain-registration', '', 'Domain Registration', '', 'Domain Registration', '', '<p>We also provide domain registration service to the individuals, companies and all kinds of businesses. We love to help individuals and companies seeking entry into the world of web by suggesting effective domain names that relate to their business profile.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As we believe the good domain names help in effective branding, attracting website visitors and credibility enhancement of companies, our domain registration service comprises of full domain registration cycle from general business analysis, finding effective domain names to hassle free domain registration.</p>\r\n', 'Domain Registration in Nepal - Register Domain - Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'domain registration in nepal, nepal domain registration', 'We provide domain registration service to the individuals, companies and all kinds of businesses & help individuals and companies seeking entry into the world of web by suggesting effective domain names', '', NULL, '', '', '2017-03-13 02:16:27', '2017-03-28 08:42:33', 1),
(30, '5', 0, '', 'Web Hosting', 'services/web-hosting', '', 'Web Hosting', '', 'Web Hosting', '', '<p>It is often problematic for companies to find a reliable hosting service provider to prevent loss of revenue, malware attacks on websites and unfavorable impacts on SEO rankings. We provide special hosting services to the companies as per the nature of their business and significance of online presence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We understand the scalability aspect of any business website and have therefore designed special hosting packages to facilitate smooth functioning of website even during high traffic and data loading. You should remember that choosing a right web hosting partner could be your most crucial business decision as many businesses have suffered significantly making a bad choice of hosting service provider.</p>\r\n', 'Web Hosting in Nepal - Affordable Nepal Web Hosting - Broadway Infosys', 'web hosting in nepal, nepal web hosting', 'We provide special hosting services to the companies as per the nature of their business and significance of online presence.', '', NULL, '', '', '2017-03-13 02:31:29', '2017-03-28 09:04:15', 1);
