ur trainees, instructors and all the stakeholders</li>\r\n		<li>We don?t hesitate to take risks and lead from the front in pressing situations</li>\r\n		<li>We believe in producing leaders rather than followers</li>\r\n		<li>We believe IT skills coupled with leadership qualities produce an unbeatable IT professional</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>We believe sense of social responsibility adds value to any business</li>\r\n		<li>We are proactive in helping the society during crisis situations</li>\r\n		<li>We make sure our trainees also become a socially responsible individual</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>To impart value-based IT knowledge and skills</li>\r\n		<li>To create employment in IT sector</li>\r\n		<li>To bridge the gap between skilled manpower and aspiring IT companies</li>\r\n		<li>To act as a platform for grooming one?s IT skill</li>\r\n		<li>To promote startup culture in Nepal</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>We attract and train the great minds</li>\r\n		<li>Our trainees are our greatest focus</li>\r\n		<li>We treat each other with respect and dignity</li>\r\n		<li>We are always committed towards producing satisfied trainees</li>\r\n		<li>Build long-term relationship with all the trainees, instructors and other stakeholders</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n\r\n	<h2>Leadership:</h2>\r\n\r\n	<h2>Social Responsibility:</h2>\r\n\r\n	<h2>Why Broadway Infosys Nepal ?</h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>While we are celebrating seven glorious years of success at Broadway Infosys here are as many reasons why you should come to this wonderland that will change yourself for the rest of your lives:</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Maintain the highest ethical standards with trainees, instructors, communities and all other stakeholders</li>\r\n		<li>Be accountable to our services and ethical practices</li>\r\n		<li>We always encourage honest feedback and suggestions regarding our services\r\n		<h2>Trust:</h2>\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>We are determined to serve the stakeholders on what matters the most</li>\r\n			<li>We have a consistent desire to improve the quality of training and win the market</li>\r\n			<li>We promote transparency in our services</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>We have a well-defined vision that is effectively communicated to our trainees, instructors and all the stakeholders</li>\r\n			<li>We don?t hesitate to take risks and lead from the front in pressing situations</li>\r\n			<li>We believe in producing leaders rather than followers</li>\r\n			<li>We believe IT skills coupled with leadership qualities produce an unbeatable IT professional</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>We believe sense of social responsibility adds value to any business</li>\r\n			<li>We are proactive in helping the society during crisis situations</li>\r\n			<li>We make sure our trainees also become a socially responsible individual</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Qualified and Experienced instructors: </strong>\r\n		<p>The instructors at Broadway bring the remarkable blend of knowledge and experience to the delight of every trainee, thus claiming the larger portion of the company?s assets. A Broadway trainer always means a smart, outspoken, innovative and a passionate team player who not only guides you to the unexplored journey of success but also walks it with you making sure you reach the destination in the most convincing way. The professionals with years of experience working with local and global IT community are passionate all the time to aware you of the career opportunities the technology guarantees and they make sure you are well positioned to grab one. So, you just make sure you come to Broadway with a genuine learning attitude and our instructors are there to lead you all along the broad WAY of success.</p>\r\n		<strong> Customized Training courses </strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>We offer time, skill and competency based courses for the trainees with specific areas of interest and proficiency. You are offered not only what you need but also what you want to excel your IT career. We are focused on serving your needs and wants and therefore we are more interested to design the training curriculum as per your demand and necessity.</p>\r\n		<strong> Sufficient training materials/resources</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>We have course wise training materials so that trainees get the required resources as per particular training curriculum. The well-equipped computer labs, qualified team of trainers, comfortable seating arrangements and other necessary etiquettes constitute a full-fledged training institute at Broadway Infosys.</p>\r\n		<strong> Value Added Learning (Learn more than what you pay for)</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>In Broadway you learn not only the ways to code smartly but also to identify and implement the right strategy to make your ideas work. The opportunity to understand the business implications of your technical ideas from our collaborators becomes a wonderful experience that guides you to play safe in this ever competitive technical business. Thus, you always take more than what you actually come here for. Here, you can always learn the crucial business logic in addition to IT logic required to implement any viable business idea.</p>\r\n		<strong> Networking:</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>We can?t escape from the ultimate truth that the businesses today survive on the foundation of network. And Broadway is more like a local IT summit where you find fellow trainees sharing similar passion and hunger to learn and innovate. It?s an exciting platform to meet and network with the experts, innovators, employers and the business players who closely work with you to explore and experiment the emerging talents that are groomed at Broadway. So, come as a stranger, learn in a team and leave with a network.</p>\r\n		<strong> Placement Opportunity</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>We ensure 100 % guarantee of job placement for outstanding learners at Broadway. We always love to find you the best company that fits perfectly to your passion and personality. Many of our alumni have been already working for the reputed companies in the country and their testimonials reflect the satisfaction they have got from Broadway?s training.</p>\r\n		<strong> Regular training evaluation</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>We have established an interactive training evaluation culture in our institute by encouraging the trainees to honestly present their feedback, suggestions and healthy criticisms to any training curriculum, resources and environment. There are very simple set of procedures to evaluate your trainers/mentors, training courses, project work supervisors and training materials. We are always committed to address your concerns and suggestions that are relevant to our regular and dedicated efforts in providing quality training to all. On the foundation of the evaluation procedures and our committed efforts in practice we are continuously working to set up an effective training control mechanism that best serves the global IT training standards.</p>\r\n\r\n		<h2>Current Scenario/Status of Job-oriented IT training in Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n		<p>As you are now familiar to the main reasons why you should join Broadway Infosys it?s important to understand the current scenario of Job-oriented IT training in Nepal for we have been committed towards improving the existing status of IT training in the country. It?s only in the recent times that the stakeholders have realized the importance of skill-based IT training in the country as a result of their counter experience with the acute shortage of skilled manpower at the times when the projects are raining. Thus, the unavailability of required manpower at the critical times is causing substantial losses to the companies as the projects go unimplemented without a qualified team. Every year thousands of IT graduates come to Nepalese job market which is already highly competitive and there is every chance of you getting rejected given the trend of giving priority to the ones with professional technical skills. And you get those skills along with the bonus ones that keep you one step ahead of your competitors all the time.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>The IT training in Nepal ranges from basic computer skills (such as MS Office package) training to hardware and computer programming skills training. As the IT knowledge and skills have potential to provide employment to anyone, the increasing number of training institutes- providing training on hardware, software, web designing, multimedia etc. - prove the wider interest of training among the educated and technically aware mass. However, the advanced computer programming training has been in existence from not long time in Nepal. These days, students are more attracted towards job-based training on PHP, JAVA, .NET, Android and iOS as the knowledge and expertise on these subject matters have great potential to provide long-term employment to the trainees considering the lack of skilled manpower in local software business. Broadway Infosys tends to solve the following problems being faced by Nepalese training institutes:</p>\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Conventional approach to training hindering innovation and creativity</li>\r\n			<li>Lack of job-oriented training courses</li>\r\n			<li>Lack of experienced instructors/trainers</li>\r\n			<li>Insufficient training materials</li>\r\n			<li>Lack of training on new and updated technologies</li>\r\n			<li>Training in isolation that prevents the trainees from networking and mutual learning</li>\r\n			<li>Lack of post-training facilities such as internship and placement for the deserving ones</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n\r\n		<p>The current status of IT training in Nepal can be reflected by the following conditions prevailing in the recent times:</p>\r\n		<strong> Lack of qualified and experienced instructors: </strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>Since most of the qualified and experienced software, mobile application development experts are engaged in professional development in IT companies there is lack of skilled and qualified instructors that are expert in their respective fields. For example, it is extremely difficult to find a knowledgeable and experienced instructor who could train the students in Android and iOS application development. Therefore, the trainees find a hard time to convince themselves regarding the potential learning and knowledge they could get from the instructors.</p>\r\n		<strong> Lack of career-focused training: </strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>The IT trainees have been feeling that most of the training courses in Nepal are designed on the basis of training institutes? surficial understanding of the particular subject matter. And it has hindered the career security of most of the trainees as they are struggling to cope with the challenging projects that are assigned by their employer. The lack of career-focused IT training has therefore further widened the gap between the IT project objectives and employees? performances.</p>\r\n		<strong> Overlooking necessity of management knowledge :</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>As the principles of management are being adopted in every sector worldwide in the recent times to ensure effective and efficient project implementation and control, the inability of training institutes to integrate management knowledge apart from core IT training has made the overall IT training incomplete and insufficient. This is the reason why most of the IT companies in Nepal are struggling with the underperformance of employees in planning, organizing and controlling the project activities. However, the number of IT graduates pursuing management degree such as MBA for their postgraduate studies is increasing gradually and this can help reduce management inefficiency of technical professionals in the long run.</p>\r\n		<strong> Dilemma of choosing the right course:</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>One of the biggest issues related to IT training in Nepal is the dilemma the trainees go through while choosing the training course. Most of them are unable to figure out what training fits them the most to pursue desired career. There has been mismatching of training courses and the competency of the trainees. Therefore the training institutes need to facilitate the aspiring trainees to choose the right training course as per their competency, learning ability and career interest.</p>\r\n		<strong> Need of Research-based Marketing techniques:</strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>Most of the training institutes in Nepal lack effective marketing techniques as they do not seem to have a proper marketing plan based on research and set of strategies to implement the plan. Thus, they end up with unsatisfied stakeholders as a consequence of marketing failures. However, the training institutes have started to realize that a well-developed marketing plan (strategies) based on logical and valid research can have rewarding impact to reach real target audience and attract the right trainees for right courses and sustain the long term relationship with all the stakeholders.</p>\r\n		<strong> Change in perspective of training: </strong>\r\n\r\n		<p>As the career scope in IT sector is increasing rapidly these days the IT trainings are pursued by not only the IT professionals but also the individuals from non-technical background that are engaged in non-technical jobs. This is an exciting opportunity for all the IT training institutes in Nepal which if capitalized could rapidly increase the training awareness and career prospects in IT sector. This could further increase the supply of skilled manpower in Nepalese IT sector that is struggling with lack of competent and skilled professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n		<h2>Benefits of Job-oriented IT training at Broadway Infosys Nepal</h2>\r\n\r\n		<p>To summarize the key reasons to join Broadway Infosys here are the 9 benefits of Job-oriented IT training in Nepal that pave the ?highway? for the trainees to reach the career destination the way Broadway does:</p>\r\n\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Learning and Earning</li>\r\n			<li>Enhanced competitiveness of IT professionals</li>\r\n			<li>Learning smart work rather than hard work</li>\r\n			<li>Regular feedback and improvement inputs</li>\r\n			<li>Learning Courses designed as per the job market needs</li>\r\n			<li>You don?t need to be a ?techie? to learn software skills</li>\r\n			<li>Learning only what is important</li>\r\n			<li>Networking with the industry professionals and experts</li>\r\n			<li>Facilitates the trainees to become the ?most wanted talent? IT companies seek</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n\r\n		<h2>Quality Training</h2>\r\n\r\n		<p>The term ?training? is defined as the ?process of bringing a person to an agreed standard of proficiency by practice and instruction?. Besides the initial qualification for the profession; knowledge, skills and competencies has to be acquired, maintained, upgraded and updated. We understand this very concept of training and are always working both harder and smarter for providing updated quality training as per the needs of the clients/students.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Our team and faculty members dedicate enough resources; time, effort, money, materials; in order to maintain and upgrade the quality we have created while providing training to the students. Practical project based learning approach, supportive teaching- learning materials/equipment, cooperative environment, effective communication between faculty, students and management, continuous evaluation, sincere attention to the feedback, positive or negative, immediate discussion and implementation of corrective actions, special focus on the overall performance; all enhances our training procedures and techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Our continuous effort on providing qualitative training can be reflected in our training system with proper training needs identification, resources assessment, competences&#39; assessment and learning outcomes, training programs design, quality assurance, certification and evaluation. In case of providing certificates also, students are required to attend exams and complete the assigned project. Supportive assistance of the instructor/trainer is available to the students even after the classes or course is over as per the faculty and students? commitment and interactions. Such eligibility and requirement criteria sets a discipline in student-teacher?s training activities with dedication in achieving the perceived goal of training.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>With 100% job assurance to the deserving students, Broadway is committed not only to prepare the students on the technical aspects but also in behavioral or personality dimensions. As we provide our students, both fresher?s and experienced, with different career opportunities, our concern is also to help them perform better right from interview to different workplace situations they might face like need of conflict handling, assertive speaking, giving presentations, preparing projects, negotiating, working in team, group discussion etc. In short, we provide soft skill training also as per the need of the students.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>So, Practical training, ready to help attitude of faculty and management, soft skills training, comfortable learning environment is equal to Broadway Quality training approach.</p>\r\n\r\n		<h2>Events:</h2>\r\n\r\n		<p>We organize regular workshops, brainstorming sessions, focus group discussions, guest lectures and talk programs with the industry experts, professionals, critics, media, private business houses and government officials to identify and analyze the existing problems and opportunities in IT sector. These events give our trainees remarkable opportunity to understand the existing IT environment in various sectors and the ways to continuously capitalize on the IT opportunities for the greater good.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Such events are designed as per the interests and opinions of our trainees so that they don?t miss out on what they want to know and learn about local and global IT environment. We have stories to share with you on how such events have inspired the public and private communities to implement IT infrastructures as a part of their operational reengineering. Also, these events have been serving as a facilitator for start-up aspirants to implement their tech ideas that have capacity to turn into a successful business venture. These events and their course changing impacts are the proof how much we are valued by our invaluable stakeholders.</p>\r\n\r\n		<p>Further, we also love to serve our society as we believe that social endeavors add value to our life. And this is the reason we don?t hesitate to organize various social events like cleaning campaign, scholarship distribution, free IT trainings to financially incapable students, relief tour to the villages struggling from natural disaster and so on. We wholeheartedly encourage our trainees to participate in social activities and gain real life experience in project management, human resource mobilization, communication skills and other essential management skills in a realistic and a fun way.</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'No. 1 Computer (IT) Training Institute in Kathmandu Nepal | Professional IT Education in Nepal', 'about broadway infosys, broadway infosys nepal, it training in nepal, computer training in nepal', 'Broadway Infosys is Nepal\'s no. 1 IT training center. It was established in 2008 and has been offering extensive range of information technology courses.', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 03:51:06', '2017-03-03 10:40:30', 1),
(2, '2', 0, 'Our Services', 'Our Services', 'Our Services', 'our-services', NULL, '<h2>Web and Software Development Training</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide extensive training on web development and software development for the aspiring developers. Our web and software development training is focused on acquainting trainees with modern practices of website development, web applications development and software development that are quality oriented and cost-effective. We understand the greater career scope for software developers worldwide and considering this fact we have designed special web development and software development training courses that address the existing and potential market needs of software industry. Our highly qualified and experienced instructors have been regularly interacting with various IT (software) companies to understand the emerging trends in software development. Understanding and analyzing the real market scenario we are continuously producing smart web developers and software developers from our focused training programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Apps Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Considering the wider usage of smartphones and increasing popularity of mobile applications we have established apps development wing that has specialized in mobile apps development for Android devices, iPhones, iPads, Windows platform etc. We provide research-based apps development service to the companies from multiple sectors prioritizing and guaranteeing genuine return on investment. Our mobile apps development wing is represented by highly qualified and experienced team of mobile application developers that are familiar to the emerging trends in apps development. Further, we also provide extensive training on mobile apps development for various popular platforms such as Android, iOS and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Software Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide software development services to every type of businesses that seek to improve their operational efficiency through implementation of software technologies. Our software development services comprise of simple application development to enterprise level applications development. The experienced developers with adequate expertise in software development have been our valuable assets for delivering the software projects as per clients&rsquo; expectations and maintaining excellent support service. With the expertise and commitment of experienced designers, developers, quality assurance engineers we make sure the right project activities are carried out in specific stages of software development life cycle. Our portfolio proves that we care about not only the software needs of the businesses but also the economic value the software guarantees for any business.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Web Development</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our expertise in web development has been reflected by the experienced web team and the portfolio it has developed till date. We provide focused web development services to the businesses that wish for impactful online presence to stay ahead of the competition. Our web development team comprising of website analysts, UX /UI designers, developers, Search Engine Optimization experts makes sure the clients generate good return on their website investment by attracting significant number of their customers online. The client testimonials and quality training on web design and development that we provide are the reflections of degree of excellence of our web development team. Should you be looking to invest on your company&rsquo;s web presence we are happy to serve you with excellence.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Web Hosting</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It is often problematic for companies to find a reliable hosting service provider to prevent loss of revenue, malware attacks on websites and unfavorable impacts on SEO rankings. We provide special hosting services to the companies as per the nature of their business and significance of online presence. We understand the scalability aspect of any business website and have therefore designed special hosting packages to facilitate smooth functioning of website even during high traffic and data loading. You should remember that choosing a right web hosting partner could be your most crucial business decision as many businesses have suffered significantly making a bad choice of hosting service provider.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Domain Registration</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We also provide domain registration service to the individuals, companies and all kinds of businesses. We love to help individuals and companies seeking entry into the world of web by suggesting effective domain names that relate to their business profile. As we believe the good domain names help in effective branding, attracting website visitors and credibility enhancement of companies, our domain registration service comprises of full domain registration cycle from general business analysis, finding effective domain names to hassle free domain registration.</p>\r\n', 'Professional IT Services by Broadway Infosys Nepal', 'IT services, professional it services, computer professional services', 'Broadway Infosys Nepal is no. 1 IT services provider ranging from web development, apps development, software development, web hosting, domain registration etc.', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 07:21:18', '2017-03-03 10:44:03', 1),
