(5, '1', 6, '', 'IT Internship in Nepal. Internship Placement by Broadway Infosys.', 'IT Internship in Nepal. ', 'internship-placement', 'INTERNSHIP/PLACEMENT', '<p>The internship facilitated by Broadway Infosys is a wonderful opportunity to test your knowledge, skills and project work experience in real work scenario. Our strong network with more than 50 IT companies in the country serves as the gateway for our trainees to enter into the real life tech world of exciting opportunities and challenges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The companies having all time rewarding corporate relationship with us regularly screen the trainees and offer them internship opportunity on the basis of their core focus, interest and skills. We ensure that every trainee gets a chance to learn from the top players in local as well as global IT business and they become genuinely competitive before starting tech career in their specific field of choice. And remember, the internship programs arranged for our trainees are mostly paid; it&rsquo;s a bonus for you in addition to valuable knowledge, skills and experience you get during the internship period.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Basically, our internship program revolves around the following core objectives:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To groom the technical, interpersonal , and informational skills of the trainees</li>\r\n	<li>To provide enabling environment for trainees to learn the most from experienced mentors</li>\r\n	<li>To make the trainees accustomed with the organizational culture</li>\r\n	<li>To impart professionalism and leadership qualities in trainees</li>\r\n	<li>To make interns understand the basic concept of project life cycle</li>\r\n	<li>To ensure the trainees are better positioned when they start their actual working career</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The aforementioned internship objectives are relevant to the trainees pursuing internship in their desired field of interest just as web application development, multimedia, mobile application development, and portal development and so on. We also categorize the trainees on the basis of level of expertise they have and the internship is planned at respective companies that could best fit their skills and personality. We make sure that our trainees are placed at the companies that could best comply with their career aspirations. The success gallery cites our achievements in this objective. Further, the events and project works that we design as per the trainees&rsquo; interests and competencies are very important tools to facilitate internships and job placements for our trainees.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '2016-10-26 07:25:07', '2017-03-08 01:21:44', 1),
(6, '0', 0, '', 'Welcome Message', 'WELCOME TO BROADWAY INFOSYS NEPAL', 'welome-to-broadway', NULL, 'Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the best inclusive computer training institutes in Kathmandu, Nepal. Established in 2008, our professional IT Training and Development center has been employing experts in this field to impart professional education to trainees. We offer well-structured complete professional training in various Programming Languages, Graphics & Multimedia, Web Designing as well as Development Training that is based upon the current recruitment needs in the IT market.', NULL, '', '', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 01:51:09', '2016-10-26 01:51:09', 1),
