(26, 17, 'Bam Bahadur Kadayat', 'bam-bahadur-kadayat', '', '', '', '<p>Positive Views about the Broadway Infosys Nepal:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Broadway Infosys provides project based Object Oriented PHP MYSQL training from real time PHP MYSQL programmers. It focuses on practical programming knowledge to produce the programmer that market demands. It is one of the finest Computer Training Institutes in Kathmandu, Nepal. It offers professional training in Programming with well managed classrooms. In my learning ,the Broadway advantage is a 100% Professional Training in programming languages.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:42:20', 0, 0, 1),
(27, 91, 'Dharmaraj Rupakheti', 'dharmaraj-rupakheti', '', '', '', '<p>I am quite impressed with Broadway Infosys Nepal&#39;s computer training technique. Their approach was completely friendly and I felt home from Day 1. The lecturer had supreme teaching skills and knowledge about the subject.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 07:48:57', 0, 0, 1),
(28, 73, 'Narahari Gautam', 'narahari-gautam', '', '', '', '<p>I was wondering here and there in Kathmandu looking for a good institute for Auto-CAD training and I finally came across Broadway Infosys Nepal and found out that it is the most ideal institution for anyone to learn Auto- CAD and be able to work like professionals do. Well equipped and furnished classroom,highly professional and dedicated teachers,helping, ever smiling,supportive and cooperative staffs, all create a great learning experience.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 07:02:16', 0, 0, 1),
(29, 73, 'Sandip Koirala', 'sandip-koirala', '', '', '', '<p>I am happy that I chose Broadway Infosys Nepal to learn Auto- CAD and recommend others also .I was able to learn more than what I expected and could work like professionals now. Proper learning environment and supportive staffs , faculty is what I need and Broadway got exactly the right thing to help create an awesome learning experience. Thanks Broadway for making me able to sought out the opportunity that is coming ahead.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 06:52:01', 0, 0, 1),
