(31, 4, 'Srijana Prajapati', 'srijana-prajapati', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is an EXCELLENT Institute which helped me to find the path towards bright future. All thanks to Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 07:28:40', 0, 0, 1),
