(33, 73, 'Kanhaiya Prasad Jayaswal', 'kanhaiya-prasad-jayaswal', '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;Yes, it&#39;s my immense pleasure getting a good platform for learning AUTO CAD in Broadway Infosys Nepal under the guidance of best teacher with every facility. It&#39;s a complete learning center.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 06:53:46', 0, 0, 1),
