(36, 7, 'Ibina Gautam', 'ibina-gautam', '/uploads/_thumbs/Images/Ibina%20Gautam-ibina.PNG', '', '', '<p>As for me, it is a better place to study. Even in short period of time, I have learnt many things which will help me for future purposes. A huge thanks to the teachers and this Institute for helping me and giving me needed knowledge about Web Design.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:49:21', 0, 0, 1),
