(41, 10, 'Suman Singh Thakuri', 'suman-singh-thakuri', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway has led me to be a Professional Graphic Designer which I wanted to be since my childhood, all credit goes to our Broadway teachers who are really helpful and understandable. They understand and solve the students&#39; problem immediately. I recommend Broadway Infosys Nepal to new comers who are really interested to do something in future or in Computer Studies.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:53:14', 0, 0, 1),
