(45, 11, 'Prabin Shahukhal', 'prabin-shahukhal', '', '', '', '<p>I felt very proud to be part of Broadway Infosys Nepal . I learned many things here. Teachers were so friendly.&nbsp;I &nbsp;am thankful to Broadway Infosys Nepal for providing me good platform to enchance my skills and knowledge and lastly I wish good luck to Broadway for the continuous success in the future too.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:57:14', 0, 0, 1),
(46, 21, 'Santosh Tandukar', 'santosh-tandukar', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is the best platform to learn IT professional education to build IT career because of availability of highly professional instructors, good management and learning environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Though not being an IT Student, I got and learned the great concept and power of Wordpress Designing and Developing.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:57:31', 0, 0, 1),
(47, 11, 'Rajat Basnet', 'rajat-basnet', '', '', '', '<p>The instructor who taught me is excellent and the best part of him is his way of teaching. And about this institution, I can say its the best place to pursue your IT knowledge and career.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:57:47', 0, 0, 1),
(48, 69, 'Ashesh Subedi', 'ashesh-subedi', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal provided me the thing i.e. PROFESSIONAL KNOWLEDGE, that I lacked. Everything including the syllabus, lectures and emphasis on concept based teaching of Broadway is quite laudable/praiseworthy. Instructive cum friendly attitude of the teacher makes the class more interesting.True concern and care for the students is the best thing about Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:59:00', 0, 0, 1),
(49, 69, 'Sunil K. Shrestha', 'sunil-k-shrestha', '', '', '', '<p>In my point of view, Broadway Infosys is one of the best IT institute. The method used for teaching here is excellent because of which I have been very confident in my knowledge of &nbsp;Dot Net. My teacher is very excellent and knows how to teach and solve my problems. So, I am very satisfied by my teacher and Broadway Infosys Nepal.<br />\r\nI think I have chosen a right institute for me as I have had the strong base for my career from this institute.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 08:59:39', 0, 0, 1),
(50, 7, 'Rachana Mandal', 'rachana-mandal', '', '', '', '<p>I feel good about my teacher and Broadway Infosys Nepal. My teacher and all other staffs are helpful and supportive here. I am glad that I learnt Web Design in this institute. Here, everything is good.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:00:05', 0, 0, 1),
(51, 1, 'Manisha Shah', 'manisha-shah', '', '', '', '<p>Our teacher and staffs here are very friendly ,kind and helpful in many ways.They help us during our class a lot and in project also.I am very glad to have such a teacher.<br />\r\nI think almost all things are available here. So,no further suggestion for improvement is needed.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:00:49', 0, 0, 1),
(52, 27, 'Lokendra Chand', 'lokendra-chand', '', '', '', '<p>While describing about Broadway Infosys Nepal, it is really a great place to study professional level programming language. The Faculty at BIN are highly talented and experts as well as teaches the students every concepts that are used in the Software Industry. After studying at BIN, now I am working in Smart Solutions Pvt. Ltd. as .Net programmer. Thanks a lot to BIN whole unit.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:01:41', 0, 0, 1),
(53, 1, 'Kishor Giri', 'kishor-giri', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal has become one of my best selection in my life. On the days of my training, I felt like home in Broadway and the mentors, the instructors here are like my parents. They have guided me in each and every steps to move forward,I would glady declare that I am one of the lucky fellow to be part of the Broadway family. Every thing here is simply awesome, go on Broadway.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:02:22', 0, 0, 1),
(54, 22, 'Sanjita Sharma', 'sanjita-sharma', '', '', '', '<p>It was a good experience studying at Broadway Infosys. I was able to gain a lot of &nbsp;knowledge on android based application. We also carried out different projects which helped to excel my study and innovate new ideas. Our sir also encouraged us to work efficiently by helping a lot in developing and learning app.<br />\r\nBroadway Infosys Nepal is an excellent computer training institute which offers programming language, web designing and many more.It has helped a lot of students who are facing difficulties in studying such training courses. So, I wish success and hope this institute will always continue the good work in the future.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:03:07', 0, 0, 1),
(55, 17, 'Keshab Pudasaini', 'keshab-pudasaini', '', '', '', '<p>It was great to join in Broadway Infosys. The teaching styles and teacher are also good. It also has a good management team. It was one of the best institution in Kathmandu valley. I would suggest all to go and join in Broadway Infosys Nepal to be good and best in Programming...!!!!!!!!</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:04:45', 0, 0, 1),
(56, 72, 'Shubham Sah', 'shubham-sah', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is faboulous. The institute is well equipped and managed. I am glad to study at Broadway. Its name is enough as everything here is broad. I am really satisfied here and I wish all the best to whole Broadway team.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:08:04', 0, 0, 1),
(57, 10, 'Sandeep Singh', 'sandeep-singh', '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;It was one of the best moment that I spent at Broadway. Really, it broadened my skill on the graphics sense.The program challenged me to think out of the box and inspired me beyond my expectations. It was very rewarding stydy in class with teachers who were knowledgeable and passionate about their work. I will forever be grateful for the individual attention given by all the faculty member of Broadway in the program. Thanks for inspiring me. Thank you Broadway.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:08:38', 0, 0, 1),
(58, 73, 'Satya Narayan Chaurasiya', 'satya-narayan-chaurasiya', '', '', '', '<p>I found the teacher best during this short span of time for exploring huge ideas and solving the queries of us/ students.. The environment at Broadway Infosys is the best and the guidance they give to students is also good .It&#39;s good to study at Broadway Infosys for better knowledge.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:09:03', 0, 0, 1),
(59, 7, 'Rakesh Ayer', 'rakesh-ayer', '', '', '', '<p>Days at Broadway was precious part of my life. The technique used in teaching, excellent premises and the family environment are core assets of this institute. This institute is the platform where students can learn to solve problems with practical exposure. And I feel privileged to be a part of Broadway Infosys Nepal. Broadway helped me to be competent with gain of practical and theoretical knowledge. The course offered and provided by Broadway with congenial environment made me alter to find out and cater the opportunity elsewhere. I am very much satisfied to complete Web Designing from here and will always be indebted with Broadway.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:10:03', 0, 0, 1),
(60, 1, 'Rakesh Ayer', 'rakesh-ayer-1', '', '', '', '<p>Along with webdesigning, I decided to study PHP training as well and it turned out to be fruitful. The technique used in teaching, excellent premises and the family environment are core assets of this institute. This institute is the platform where students can learn to solve problems with practical exposure. And I feel priviledged to be a part of Broadway Infosys Nepal. Broadway helped me to be competent with gain of practical and theoretical knowledge. The course offered and provided by Broadway with congenial environment made me alter to find out and cater the opportunity elsewhere. I am very much satisfied to complete PHP training from here and will always be indebted with Broadway.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(61, 17, 'Ramesh Pokhrel', 'ramesh-pokhrel', '', '', '', '<p>The teacher was excellent in his way of teaching the subject matter. He taught us in a friendly environment. Broadway Infosys Nepal is a good Platform in Nepal for the Information Technology Field. All the teachers here are expert in their particular field and subject. The management committee is also concerned for the student&#39;s better performance in their subject matter providing friendly environment.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:11:47', 0, 0, 1),
(62, 17, 'Kshitiz Karmacharya', 'kshitiz-karmacharya', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is very good institute. The instructor was really great in teaching and learning environment here was awesome. The practical exposure while studying and carrying out real time projects made me understand every course content in detail . I would like to get some other training as well.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:14:09', 0, 0, 1),
(63, 7, 'Shriya Sharma', 'shriya-sharma', '', '', '', '<p>The institute as well as my teacher was very helpful to me in solving all my problems and queries during the entire course. I have learned a lot and learned in practical approach.<br />\r\nI would like to thank the institute for conducting such courses.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:14:58', 0, 0, 1),
(64, 1, 'Nakul Rayamajhi', 'nakul-rayamajhi', '', NULL, NULL, '<p>I am very happy that I joined this institute for my training of PHP/MySQL. Our instructor guided us very well, his instruction and timing given to the students was really excellent and I appreciate Broadway for providing such friendly and talented teacher.&nbsp;I would suggest Broadway to continue such environment and my best wishes shall always be with Broadway for its future progress.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:45', 0, 0, 1),
(65, 91, 'Binod  Mehta', 'binod-mehta', '', '', '', '<p>I am very glad to be a student of this institution and my special thanks to counselor , the instructor and whole&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/broadwayinfosys\">Broadway Infosys</a>&nbsp;family for helping me start my career in Java. The approach of teaching Java by the instructor is really awesome and am realy thankful for helping me carrying out my project so well.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:18:33', 0, 0, 1),
