(68, 17, 'Umesh  Sujakhu', 'umesh-sujakhu', '', NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.76px;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the finest IT Institute that can make you able to learn various basic and professional computer related courses with programming. So if you are seeking a platform to learn it then you can visit here. Instructors and administration are friendly and you can get a better future..</span></p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:45', 0, 0, 1),
