(71, 22, 'Srijan  Chand ', 'srijan-chand', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the most Dedicated IT Training institute in Kathmandu valley and really focus on generating mass as well as quality IT intellectuals. And I Joined this Institute to shape my future IT Carrier and its really really going great...</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:29:14', 0, 0, 1),
(72, 22, 'Upendra Bikram Thapa ', 'upendra-bikram-thapa', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is the best platform for the pioneers interested in getting involved into the virtual world of Information technology.<br />\r\nThe best in the town and also taught by the best person in the related fields.<br />\r\nThus providing with the complete reference into the subject matter of choice, turning the trainee into a professional work-person.<br />\r\nExcellent facilitated workspace for the students with friendly faculty members.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:30:19', 0, 0, 1),
(73, 22, 'Satya  Prakash Joshi', 'satya-prakash-joshi', '', '', '', '<p>One of best IT computer training &nbsp;institute in kathmandu Nepal is Broadway Infosys Nepal. Learning Android course at this institute was my best decision ever as it has helped me to shape my career in Android.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:31:33', 0, 0, 1),
(75, 69, 'Binod Yadav  ', 'binod-yadav', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway provided me the thing i.e. PROFESSIONAL KNOWLEDGE, that I lacked. Everything including the syllabus, lectures and emphasis on concept based teaching of Broadway is quite laudable/praiseworthy. Instructive cum friendly attitude of the teacher makes the class more interesting.True concern and care for the students is the best thing about Broadway Infosys Nepal</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 13:42:40', 0, 0, 1),
(76, 27, 'Naresh Chaudhary ', 'naresh-chaudhary', '', '', '', '<p>While describing about Broadway Infosys Nepal, it is really a great place to study professional level programming language. The Faculty at BIN are highly talented and experts as well as teaches the students every concepts that are used in the Software Industry. After studying at BIN, now I am working in Smart Solutions Pvt. Ltd. as .Net programmer. Thanks a lot to Broadway Infosys Nepal whole unit.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:32:37', 0, 0, 1),
(77, 92, 'Softskilltraining Nepal', 'softskilltraining-nepal', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway........the name itself is enough to say about the institute.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExperienced, well qualified real time instructors; supportive teaching-learning equipments, materials,cooperativeness, effective, sincere, continuous, timely communication, ready to help attitude of every staff, faculty, management;parental guidance, no sign of ignorance in any issue, small or big;positive acceptance and response in feedback, positive or negative...<br />\r\nWhat else to say....? Broadway Infosys Nepal is always focused in providing quality effective IT training to every students and is committed for outstanding results....<br />\r\nSo, BIN has reached broad way and is committed to contribute for the nation in the same manner.... Go ahead Broadway.............:)</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:34:22', 0, 0, 1),
(78, 11, 'Pramod Prajapati', 'pramod-prajapati', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is a good &amp; excellent institute ..... it comprises of&nbsp; friendly and cooperative learning environment and the training&nbsp; gives us more infomation...... its a best institute for me... you can visit here for studying your desired IT course and I can assure you for the best results.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:37:10', 0, 0, 1),
(80, 92, 'Joshan  Gurung', 'joshan-gurung', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway infosys is the professional training center. I found here qualified and experienced teachers as well as open educational environment. So, I chose Broadway Infosys Nepal for studying Groovy and Grails and the result came out with flying colours. .</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:38:48', 0, 0, 1),
(81, 92, 'Shyam Acharya ', 'shyam-acharya', '', '', '', '<p>In broadway there is excellent environment for learning and gaining a lot in IT sector .I came to know about Broadway Infosys from my friend and came along with him to study here and I must say it is the best institute for learning this course.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:40:42', 0, 0, 1),
(82, 3, 'Santosh Joshi ', 'santosh-joshi', '', '', '', '<p>I feel Broadway is the best place for one&#39;s bright and successful career. One can get opportunity to develop a lot in the field of his interest in information technology&nbsp; when enrolled into Broadway Infosys as it serves as a great finishing school..</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:42:44', 0, 0, 1),
(83, 10, 'Bicky Chaudhary', 'bicky-chaudhary', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is really a best institute situated in Kathmandu which provides a professional training for any level of student. All the members of this institute are co-operative and friendly and it has helped me a lot to overcome the problem arousen during the learning. So thanks to the institute, teacher, staffs and all members.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 06:09:10', 0, 0, 1),
