(85, 27, 'Gagan Mudvari ', 'gagan-mudvari', '', '', '', '<p>If you finished your degree in IT field .. you should go broadway infosys once. They provide such useful training and 100% job assurance also. I really learned and gained a lot.... well done.. keep it up .. Broadway Infosys Nepal .</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:44:35', 0, 0, 1),
(86, 7, 'Ramesh Pokhrel ', 'ramesh-pokhrel-1', '', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal really comes to be the good partner of the IT lovers. The real IT starts here if anybody want to be sharp knowledge person within their related IT field. Real time worked experienced instructor became the first attraction point as far as my experience expressed, secondly all the necessary infrastructure for the good learning environment makes me well comfort there. All the management committee here provides good hospitality that makes you experiencing free of cost learning center in Nepal.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWanna wish for its excellent future.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 09:46:04', 0, 0, 1),
