(92, 8, 'Sadikshya Adhikari ', 'sadikshya-adhikari', '/uploads/testimonials/sd.jpg', '', '', '<p><br />\r\nit&#39;s learning environment is a memorable and astounding experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Broadway is really a great professional IT training and development company. I have found myself and everyone associated here having outstanding learning and working experiences. Being a part of Broadway team and it&#39;s learning environment would be a memorable and astounding experience.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 02:55:20', 0, 0, 1),
