(106, 34, 'Vivek Ratna Kansakar', 'vivek-ratna-kansakar', '/uploads/Vivek%20Ratna%20Kansakar.jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the professional institute for learning coding. The teachers in Broadway are expert in their respective fields and easy to communicate with. The learning/training method is also interactive and the learning environment is also good &amp; positive. Broadway also provides job placement feature for its eligible students at renowned IT companies in Nepal. I studied Laravel Framework and have gained a great deal of knowledge from this institute and also have joined a reputable company through Broadway. I suggest Broadway to anyone who wants to learn Web Development for job purpose. Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 10:10:31', 0, 0, 1),
(107, 90, 'AJUSHA RIZAL', 'ajusha-rizal', '/uploads/testimonials/AJUSHA%20RIZAL%20teat.jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is the gateway to enter the IT software industry. I should specifically mention the support given to me by the faculty. The curriculum is well-structured and matches real-time projects. It is updated and their lab facility is an added advantage where we can acquire practical knowledge. I also want to take this opportunity to thank our teacher Mr. Yadav Raj Ojha for such wonderful class. You have been so direct and so honest in teaching us vital information about important issues that revolve around the IT field. You have made it so constructive and easy to learn in that it truly has made a difference in the way I look at programming now. Thank you for a wonderful support... Broadway Infosys Nepal .</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 10:25:43', 0, 0, 1),
(108, 90, 'Jagat Man Mulguthi ', 'jagat-man-mulguthi', '/uploads/testimonials/jagat%20testi.jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal , as name implies it is a high way to get trained in technological skills. Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the leading and successful IT training institutes that have satisfied all of the IT enthusiast&rsquo;s students to acquire various IT skills. I joined the Broadway in 2012 for Web Development Training and till now I have trained here with many IT skills. One of my favorite things that attracts me all the time is: the friendly management and expert IT Instructors. Aside from educating me in IT skills, Broadway Infosys Nepal&nbsp;has counseled and has assisted me in acquiring getting job. However comes to me for IT training, Broadway Infosys Nepal is my first list of selection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 10:26:51', 0, 0, 1),
(109, 90, 'Anil kr Sah ', 'anil-kr-sah', '/uploads/testimonials/Anil%20testi%20-min.jpg', '', '', '<p>The future depends on what you do today. I feel Broadway Infosys Nepal serves as a bridge way between my academic life to career life. The most important aspect of Broadway Infosys Nepal is its teachers and management.Teachers are very friendly and professionals. I feel proud joining Broadway Infosys Nepal &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 10:27:57', 0, 0, 1),
(110, 96, 'Jen Bati', 'jen-bati', '/uploads/testimonials/Jen%20Bati-min.jpg', '', '', '<p>Gaining professional skills in Microsoft .Net programming language (C#, ASP.NET, MS-SQL) at this fine institution was a boon for me.<br />\r\nI have been to several IT academic institutions both overseas and in Nepal.Through internet research, I found out about Broadway infosys Institute, I learned more comfortable and Quality latest technology tools with Specialist teacher Multiple software Development teachers.Compared to other IT Institute, Broadway is really good. Here, I studied Advance Web Designing, Advance Wordpress and Advance SEO (Search Engine Optimization) Development .I am thinking to study more IT courses again. And I would highly recommend Broadway Infosys Nepal to everyone who is interested to take training in any IT course Thank you for all Broadways Infosys Nepal Team.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 10:33:53', 0, 0, 1),
(111, 90, 'Sanjok  Khakurel ', 'sanjok-khakurel', '/uploads/testimonials/sanjok%20ji%20web-min.jpg', '', '', '<p>Java training in Nepal by <strong>Broadway Infosys</strong> is one of the best in the country. I truly believe that Broadway Infosys Nepal is a &ldquo;Broadway Infosys Nepal&rdquo; where fresher college graduates, absolute beginners and other personalities can walk to go to their ultimate destination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After completion of the course I found myself into a new level of programming world. Well organized and knowledge oriented course, highly qualified and experienced trainer, well maintained lab and peaceful environment has really given me new courage insight and energy to reach up to my destination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is an experience that will live long in my memory. I want to express my gratitude to my course instructor for carrying out this challenging program so effectively. Thank you for the opportunity and warm support Broadway Infosys Nepal family.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 10:35:20', 0, 0, 1),
(112, 25, 'Rabin Gurung', 'rabin-gurung', '/uploads/testimonials/rabin%20web-min.jpg', '', '', '<p>IT training in Broadway Infosys Nepal has been one of the best choice for my career.<br />\r\nI have been to several IT institutes and found Broadway Infosys Nepal&nbsp;to be one of the best IT Institutes. Comfortable learning, Quality Latest course updates,&nbsp;multiple software development instructors makes Broadway distinguished from other IT&nbsp;Institute. I took Java, Advance Web Designing, Advance Wordpress and Advance SEO (Search Engine Optimization) Development from Broadway Infosys Nepal. Thank you&nbsp;Broadways Infosys Nepal team for excellent service.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 11:22:15', 0, 0, 1),
(113, 39, 'Rekha Bohara', 'rekha-bohara', '/uploads/testimonials/rekha%20web%20page.jpg', '', '', '<p>In IT,&nbsp;here if anything that matter most &nbsp;is skill , Being IT student I always have passion towards programming and Broadway Infosys turned my that passion &nbsp;into skill. To choose Broadway &nbsp;is one of my best decision. 24/7 running classes on each and every new technology, amazing &nbsp;managerial management skill of Uttam sir, best management team, selected best experience teacher, I found Broadway more than my expectations. they don&#39;t only help you to sharpen your skill but also help you to establish your career in best companies around the world. At first I &nbsp;came to Broadway empty handed just holding a &nbsp;passion for IOS but in return I found hand full of opportunities . Broadway helped me to step my career path in professional world . It turned my dream into reality.It provides young fresh students a platform &nbsp;to rise their skill and &nbsp;achieve their dreams. I really appreciate how they are doing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 11:26:34', 0, 0, 1),
(114, 1, 'Feroz Siwakoti', 'feroz-siwakoti', '/uploads/testimonials/Feroz%20Siwakoti%20web%20(1).jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the Pioneer IT learning institute. The methods and approach of teaching in Broadway is very commendable. The institute provides a definite productive gateway by interlinking the bridge between the learned foundations in college academics to the real world industrial applicable projects.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 11:35:09', 0, 0, 1),
(115, 34, 'Yamendra Pun ', 'yamendra-pun', '/uploads/testimonials/pun%20web%20.jpg', '', '', '<p>If you are looking for professional IT training, then Broadway Infosys Nepal &nbsp;is the best. I had an opportunity to learn Laravel Framework at Broadway Infosys Nepal. I found the teachers are supportive and friendly so learning is always fun. The teaching methods at BIN is industry oriented and the best practices used by current IT companies. I would like to thank our instructor for his exceptional time and effort to make our class more professional. He is always willing to teach new things and help us in every way possible. Apart from this Broadway Infosys Nepal has best management team. They are always willing to help and guide you. I feel so proud to be part of Broadway Infosys Nepal family.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 11:35:50', 0, 0, 1),
(116, 7, 'Roshan Tamang', 'roshan-tamang', '/uploads/testimonials/Roshan%20Tamang.jpg', '', '', '<p>To Broadway Infosys Nepal,<br />\r\nIn order to utilize the three months of gap after my SLC examination, I was in great confusion what to do. My all other friends already had joined bridge courses language classes and some basic computer classes. I felt like I was in too last among my friends. I wanted to develop some IT skills in that period. Therefore, I spent many times in search of computer training institute in Kathmandu. I found a unique institute named &lsquo;Broadway Infosys Nepal&rsquo; when I searched for the institute. Its responsive website fascinated me. Then the testimonials of ex-students inspired me to join Broadway.<br />\r\nThe journey of two months with Broadway in Web Design and C&amp; c++ Programming was unforgettable and very interesting. Qualified and experienced instructors led me to perfection in my related field. I&rsquo;m highly satisfied with each and every moment spent with Broadway. Fast internet and 24 hours power supply played very important contribution for the training. It helped to run the practical activities along with learning theoretical knowledge&rsquo;s. Perfect guidance, feedback and interaction of my teachers made me feel like home and I&rsquo;m being taught by my own friends. I didn&rsquo;t get notice of spending two months with Broadway.<br />\r\nFor new students or people who want to gain or improve their IT skill, I want to advise them to join Broadway. It is the team of qualified, professional and experienced instructors and staff. It gives quality of knowledge and guides perfectly to way of related IT field where you want to make your career at moderate payment. It offers various subjects like Web Design, AutoCAD, Java, Android etc.. It not only gives knowledge, it offers for internships or jobs after training for the students.<br />\r\nI&rsquo;m proud of being a student of Broadway Infosys Nepal. I liked its all facil