(117, 90, 'Rishabh Jha', 'rishabh-jha', '/uploads/testimonials/Rishabweb%20jha.jpg', '', '', '<p>Being a B. tech Computer science student, I always had<br />\r\npassion towards learning more of Computer programming courses and Broadway Infosys Nepal has helped me out in this.<br />\r\nTo choose Broadway is one of my best decision so far. 24/7 running classes on each and every new technology oriented course, skilled &amp; friendly teachers makes it exceptional.<br />\r\nThe difference between extra ordinary &amp; ordinary is that little &quot;extra&quot;.So to be extraordinary, join today &amp; get an opportunity to be as more than you know or as u are capable off in Broadway Infosys Nepal just as I could understand the difference between ordinary &amp; extra ordinary by joining here.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 11:46:41', 0, 0, 1),
