(124, 91, 'PRAKASH BIST', 'prakash-bist', '/uploads/testimonials/prakash%20web.jpg', '', '', '<p>I choose to learn from the best. When it comes to learning how to code, Broadway is the place where I find freedom to learn coding. I have always had an interest in working as a java programmer. I consider myself extremely fortunate that I made the choice to study java programming at Broadway. It has always been encouraging to learn beyond the abilities and for me Broadway has played substantial role in my career development. Obviously, I would like to say that Broadway is the institution where I learned career oriented knowledge in very short period of time. The skills I have gained through the course have equipped me to accomplish my professional goal. I would like to thank the entire Broadway family for providing such a wonderful platform for people like me. I hope it continues to produce more professionals in the days ahead.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:08:48', 0, 0, 1),
(125, 17, 'RAVI SHARMA BASTOLA', 'ravi-sharma-bastola', '/uploads/uploads/rrrrr(2).jpg', '', '', '<p>BroadWay Infosys is the only institute in Nepal where you learn the techniques to tackle the problem. The main focus in Broadway Infosys is to solve the problem with creativity instead of copying the solution. I wanted to start an IT career but did not know where to start. Broadway gave me the platform from where I began to see my career clearly and I am thankful to them for that. All of the staff , the teachers are helpful and the teaching techniques are reviewed on the monthly basis by the teachers to meet the latest demands of the industry. I hope Broadway will continuously help students reach their desired careers as they did to me . Thanks To BROADWAY INFOSYS NEPAL</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 02:45:03', 0, 0, 1),
(126, 21, 'PRAMOD THAKUR', 'pramod-thakur', '/uploads/uploads/pramod%20web(2).jpg', '', '', '<p>First of all , I am very very thankful to my teacher who taught me. He is a very good instructor. His teaching style is very simple, conceptual, logical and more effective. He always smiles in difficult situation and handles problem in easy way. He always guides the latest concept and new technology. So thanks for not making us learn the way you wanted to teach, but teaching us the way we wanted to learn. I think &quot;Technology has made it easier for students to learn with new devices , but nothing can come close to the experience of being taught by an inspirational teacher like him&quot;.<br />\r\nBroadway Infosys Nepal is a No.1 training center in Nepal; they always launch new professional skills as well as more effective, conceptual and dynamic teachers. They always help those students who want to improve their professional skills. I have heard Broadway Infosys Nepal giving job opportunity to deserving students, yes they give but at the same time, Broadway Infosys Nepal gives good quality study to their students. I am feeling very proud and lucky to join Broadway Infosys Nepal. So thanks for going out of your way and teaching me life&rsquo;s lessons which I have never learnt from textbooks and reference books. Thanks to all members of Broadway Infosys Nepal who guided me, taught me and gave me a big opportunity and heartily thanks to Mr. Utam Adhikari</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:13:40', 0, 0, 1),
