(128, 1, 'Hari Bhurtel', 'hari-bhurtel', '/uploads/uploads/hari%20sir.jpg', '', '', '<p>When you are in search of IT professional training center in Nepal, Broadway Infosys is the best place. I found excellent environment here to learn latest IT courses. I came here to gain some knowledge about Word Press without reference but via website visit. I wondered in the beginning with some doubt about the fulfillment of my target. But as I started learning with core PHP, my doubt nullified from the very first day. The teachers, I found very supportive and friendly. All teachers have excellent command in their subject and are kind human person. To care every student is not too easy task but caring one by one is classic. Class with next generation was new experience for me which is more fantastic and enjoyable. On the other hand, all the teachers who hit me for six touched to my heart about their effort to make perfect every student in their professional life. This assurance of sharing knowledge even after the completion of the course is another valuable thought to mention here which are unforgettable to me. I believe, every teacher of the Institute must be of same class, same category. Also the management team of the Institute which I found is very nice with hard working and caring attitude. I would like to thank all the person of the Institute with whom I involved directly. I wish Broadway Infosys Nepal to be a brand globally in the years to come.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:15:41', 0, 0, 1),
(129, 7, 'Mo Bah', 'mo-bah', '/uploads/usa.jpg', '', '', '<p>I took the Web Design Training at Broadway Infosys Nepal 7 years back and Broadway Infosys Nepal gave me the best of what I required to add up to my IT career. I later designed many websites around the world and presently doing much of web design for lots of customer from the USA and other countries.<br />\r\nThanks to Broadway Infosys Nepal. I have become a professional today.<br />\r\nI recommend any person keen to start up their career in IT just to run down to Broadway Infosys Nepal for their dreams to come to reality.<br />\r\nGod bless the team out there.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:16:39', 0, 0, 1),
(130, 22, 'Aashish Dahal ', 'aashish-dahal', '/uploads/aashish%20dahal%20android.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px;\">For many people like me, who were roaming different institutes for professional training, Broadway Infosys Nepal was like heaven. I was young, energetic and was eager to learn technology and trust me, Broadway Infosys Nepal is the place where you could invest your time to build professionalism within yourself. Enormous support from mentors, teachers and as well as faculty member<span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"font-family: inherit; display: inline;\">s helps a lot to build capacity in you and make you successful. Broadway Infosys Nepal has a great learning environment where healthy interactions and learning goes side by side. I am very much satisfied by what Broadway Infosys Nepal has given me and will always be thankful to all the teachers and staffs. What I am today, is all because of Broadway Infosys Nepal. Thank you very much.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:46', 0, 0, 1),
(131, 34, 'KUMAR SUBEDI', 'kumar-subedi', '/uploads/kumar.jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the best software training institute. It gives the best what we require to develop our career with best IT course. The excellent environment, experienced teacher is key part of it. I was so unconscious and distracted about my future. But I found Broadway Infosys Nepal which has been helping me for IT training to lead right way.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:18:21', 0, 0, 1),
(132, 17, 'Surya Pachhai Chhetri ', 'surya-pachhai-chhetri', '/uploads/uploads/surya.jpg', 'Suriya', 'suriya pachhai chhetri', '<p>&quot;I joined Broadway Infosys Nepal for Advance PHP. Faculties here has real time work experience and that&#39;s the plus point and the instructor here are highly experienced . They show patience to clear all the doubts that comes in students mind. We can take the classes repeatedly and also take back-up classes. No restriction are there with the teaching methodology here. Totally, a good institute for learners,fresher and job seekers. By gaining knowledge from Broadway now I am in a senior position of PHP developer in one of the reputed IT Company in Nepal&quot;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:19:29', 0, 0, 1),
(133, 22, 'Bibek Shrestha ', 'bibek-shrestha', '/uploads/uploads/bibek.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>I am very grateful towards this institute. It&rsquo;s like a home to me as all faculty are like part of a family. IT is a simple term but you should keep on updating yourself to the technology even if you know the basics. Learning every new thing is gaining something for yourself. In IT field , one is recognized in terms of skill, knowledge, coding and approach to learn more and this is the very basic component. I found all the essentials on Broadway Infosys Nepal. I think Broadway is the best institute you can find to upgrade your talent from beginner level to mid or high level. Here, I never got bored learning different courses like android, C#.net, java, etc. You can find any updated course here so that you can update your level as well. I find Broadway Infosys Nepal family supportive, co-operative and helping in any area you need. I found that teachers here are really talented working on industry to lead you here with appropriate contents. Thus, If you are looking for database, software or web designing , then you are welcome to the Broadway infosys Nepal Family.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:46', 0, 0, 1),
(134, 3, 'Uday Pandit ', 'uday-pandit', '/uploads/uploads/Uday%20Pandit.jpg', '', '', '<p>If anyone thinks about to make the career in IT field, just opt Broadway Infosys Nepal. It is one of the best IT training centers in Nepal and also provides job opportunity to deserving students. It has been well facilitated with Computer lab, qualified and experienced Trainer from different IT industries. I had been looking IT training center in Kathmandu for Microsoft.NET Package Training. Finally, I found Broadways Infosys Nepal and joined it. I learned there to develop Desktop Application and Web Application using C# and ASP.NET respectively. Though I am from Electrical Engineering Background ,I did not find any difficulties during the training. Here, teachers are very helpful and problem-solving towards every student. Those who are fresh in IT field, even they can learn programming smoothly. The trainer has an excellent methodology to train the students even if they belong to different educational background. Teachers are also updating technologies from IT field towards students.<br />\r\nNow I have confident to build Desktop based as well as Web-based Application using C#, Asp.Net and Microsoft SQL Server.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThank You very much Broadway Infosys Nepal, for giving me a platform to boost my career in IT field.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:22:46', 0, 0, 1),
(135, 21, 'Himal Dhoj Malla ', 'himal-dhoj-malla', '/uploads/testimonials/himal%20dhoj%20malla.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>East or West, &quot;Broadway Infosys Nepal&quot; is the best IT professional institute of Nepal due to its locality, well managed lab, highly experienced instructors, modern teaching and training methodology, helpful management and good environment. Being a computer engineer, I have taken 5 professional webpage designing and development trainings from Broadway and am still continuing. Come and Learn, Go and Earn. This is what I can Guarantee from Broadway Infosys Nepal&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:46', 0, 0, 1),
(137, 85, 'Bimal Prasad Pandey', 'bimal-prasad-pandey', '/uploads/testimonials/bimal.jpg', '', '', '<p>The field of information technology is vast and complex, so we have to choose institute that help us to cope with complexity. Broadway Infosys Nepal&#39;s strategy involves delivering a broad and diverse foundation of coursework with highly experienced teachers and well infrastructure, even allowing students the opportunity of internship after course completion. The program is also highly flexible and offers student multiple starting dates and flexible course loads to accommodate even the busiest of schedules.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 07:16:10', 0, 0, 1),
(138, 61, 'Sonam Dema', 'sonam-dema', '/uploads/testimonials/Sonam%20D%20Dema.jpg', '', '', '<p>My stay here in this institute for last 2 weeks was very short one but the impact I am taking home through knowledge and ideas are of vast depth. It was all possible because of the well executed efforts and help rendered by the institute. I would like to take this time to express my heartfelt gratitude to the instructor and the whole team of this wonderful institute.I owe a lot to the my instructor for his full time support and powerful guidance during this whole course.I am glad that I have undergone a course with this institute for I am now in better position to deal with linux. I will never forget the touching hospitality and warm treatment that I received from this institute and Nepal as a whole. I also want to extend my gratitude to my office MFA(Ministry of Foreign Affairs),Thimphu,Bhutan for selecting me and making this happen. Thanks one and all...</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:24:18', 0, 0, 1),
(139, 22, 'Ankit Adhikari ', 'ankit-adhikari', '/uploads/testimonials/Ankit%20Adhikari.jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is a best institute for IT enthusiast who is seeking to build his or her career in a better way. &nbsp;Filled with highly equipped technologies and friendly behavior of highly trained professionals, Broadway helps us to know about the course deeply thus resulting in 100% output. If I have to suggest, the only institute that pops up in my mind for IT courses is Broadway Infosys Nepal. Why should one roam everywhere when you have Broadway Infosys as one stop solution.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:33:29', 0, 0, 1),
(141, 34, 'Prince Chaurasiya', 'prince-chaurasiya', '/uploads/uploads/prince-min%20-%20Copy.png', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the best institute in Nepal I have ever found. I can proudly say that there is no better institute than Broadway. It is totally different than others since you will get experienced friendly learning environment with highly experienced teachers and well infrastructure. I am so very lucky and feel glad that I am student from Broadway. I am so much grateful and have lot of respect towards this institute and teachers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The time I spent and learnt will always be one of the best and memorable experience in my life since I felt environment of learning so caring, supportive, helpful and much more like home. The way parents take care, support and help, I felt the same with the teachers and staffs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Throughout my life, I was searching for teacher whom I can say that &hellip;YES &hellip;this is the one who is my favorite and best teacher and that teacher I got from this institute. &nbsp;Our sir was so helpful, supportive, hardworking and highly experienced. So, I strongly recommend everyone to join, learn and reach the level of excellence with Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-20 12:42:07', 0, 0, 1),
(142, 21, 'Ruben Khadgi', 'ruben-khadgi', '/uploads/testimonials/rubin.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>Being an IT student, I got a chance to learn from different IT institutes but none of them came close to Broadway Infosys Nepal. It is one of the best IT training institutes in Nepal. I insist everyone who want to learn IT related courses to join Broadway. Best Management, Best Learning Environment , Best Instruction, Best service and Best guarantee of Best career......!!!</p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:46', 0, 0, 1),
(143, 17, 'Sachin Hamal', 'sachin-hamal', '/uploads/uploads/Sachin%20Hamal%201.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the best IT training institute in Nepal.This institute is helping Nepali as well as international students to get quality training in reasonable price and is eventually assisting Nepal to raise it&#39;s standard in IT sector.<br />\r\nI am very happy to be part of Broadway Infosys Nepal for some period .I found all the staffs of this institute very friendly and they are always ready to assist you.Teachers here are experienced and efficient enough to teach in the way that student can learn quickly. I would be very happy to recommend Broadway Infosys to everyone who are thinking and willing &nbsp;to make career in IT field.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-06 08:09:46', 0, 0, 1),
(144, 6, 'Manzeel Uprety', 'manzeel-uprety-1', '/uploads/testimonials/1490065611.jpg', '', '', '<p>Broadway Infoys Nepal is one of the best IT learning center in Kathmandu. Well equipped infrastructure and highly skilled trainers makes Broadway infosys Nepal is a perfect place for IT training in Nepal. My training experience in QA along with Oracle was great fun and I am sure to work professionally in these matter.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(145, 91, 'Monika Bhatt', 'monika-bhatt', '/uploads/testimonials/1490065331.jpg', '', '', '<p>Studying any kind of IT related training has never been more accessible than it is now. However, amongst the wide range of competitive IT training institutes in Nepal, Broadway Infosys is undoubtedly the best when it comes to understanding and attainment of practical knowledge. The extremely helpful management and teachers, make training feel like a fun filled activity. I highly recommend all graduates to undertake IT related training in Broadway for proper future job prospects.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(146, 91, 'Dagina Basnet ', 'dagina-basnet', NULL, '', '', '<p>&quot;Broadway Infosys, one of the reputed IT training institute of Nepal offers you a training on any one of the course of your interest with <strong>100% scholarship</strong> because of your good academic performance.&quot; When I got this message from my teacher, I was really happy because it was like an encouragement and a great support to me. I would like to thank Broadway Infosys Nepal for this wonderful opportunity. I feel very lucky to be a part of this institute and I must say Broadway is the best place to learn IT related courses. It is well managed place with good learning environment, experienced instructors and a good teaching methodology. The instructor here are very supportive, friendly and dedicated towards the students because of which student can learn smoothly and in the way they want. You will never regret spending your time, money and energy while you are in Broadway. Also, this institute helps to encourage and lift up the good students providing scholarships and special discounts. So, I would like to recommend Broadway infosys to anyone who is willing to make their career in the field of IT. Lastly, I would personally like to thank Raju Adhikari sir, Uttam Adhikari sir, Dhiraj Kumar Jha sir and Orchid International College for showing their concern towards me and for their effort to make a better me.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(147, 91, 'Subina Khanal', 'subina-khanal', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is the best IT training institute for beginners and experienced professionals in Nepal. The course content and reference docs are good and the best thing is the way instructor explains each topic with live demonstrations and examples. The environment at Broadway Infosys is the best and the guidance they give to students is also good. It&rsquo;s good to study at Broadway Infosys for better knowledge. Also, I feel very glad to be selected as one of the scholar of this institute being provided with <strong>100% scholarship</strong>. I will forever be grateful for the individual attention given by all the faculty members of Broadway in the program. Thanks for inspiring me. Thank you, Broadway.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(148, 21, 'Bipin Karna', 'bipin-karna', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway infosys Nepal is one of the best IT leading education in Nepal.It is best platform to build career in IT sector. It lets you to put your thoughts together in a very concise format.It really helps you present your best face. I studied Laravel, Php and WordPress training and am satisfied in all.I am proud to be part of Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(149, 17, 'Ritesh Lamichhane', 'ritesh-lamichhane', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys, I say it&rsquo;s the best IT training center among all simply because of its career oriented training and planned syllabus taught by professional and well experienced instructors which help students face the real-time working environment with less problems. Of course, I can&rsquo;t forget it&rsquo;s continuous career guidance and support to its students from instructors as well as management even after training period is over.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(150, 11, 'Eriz Rai', 'eriz-rai', NULL, '', '', '<p>I&#39;m so much fascinated by all the services offered/provided in Broadway Infosys. Most of all, the training packages are completely practically based, very affordable as compared to other IT training centers and is located in the heart of Kathmandu where transportation is readily available from anywhere in the valley. They&#39;ve got the best teachers with Higher Degree Certificates and many years of experience. The entire management team is very friendly and humble. They try their best for each and every student to cover their whole lessons even if they missed it. I recommend all of my juniors, seniors and contemporary friends to explore the world of Information Technology. Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(151, 27, 'Binod Yadav', 'binod-yadav-1', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway provided me the thing i.e. PROFESSIONAL KNOWLEDGE, that I lacked. Everything including the syllabus, lectures and emphasis on concept based teaching of Broadway is quite laudable/praiseworthy. Instructive cum friendly attitude of the teacher makes the class more interesting.True concern and care for the students is the best thing about Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(152, 25, 'Pramod Satyal', 'pramod-satyal', NULL, '', '', '<p>My overall experience of learning here at Broadway Infosys Nepal has been really great and effective. I really wanted to learn about SEO as it is one of the most important digital marketing tool in the competitive world of e-commerce and this training proved to be really beneficial for me. The instructor was really good and I was quite impressed by his way of teaching making it fun and interesting. I enjoyed working in my different assignments and have really learned a lot. The Broadway team is also equally supportive and friendly. I would strongly recommend anyone who wants to learn about SEO or any other IT training course as I am leaving satisfied from here and so will you.&rdquo;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(153, 25, 'Rakhi Basnet', 'rakhi-basnet', NULL, '', '', '<p>&ldquo;Learning at Broadway has been really worthy and accomplishing. I got to learn a lot and at the same time already working at SEO. All thanks to Broadway team. The learning environment is really friendly, comfortable, warm and co-operative. God Bless Broadway&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(154, 82, 'Prakash Tandukar', 'prakash-tandukar', NULL, '', '', '<p>&ldquo;Being a civil engineering student, I really got benefitted by taking training from Broadway. It helped me a lot in my project too. At first, I was uncertain if the course would be fruitful for me or not. However, after strong assurance of the counselor and excellent execution of the training session by the professional engineer himself, I was happy. I would really declare Broadway Infosys Nepal as one of the best training institute in Nepal for IT training.&rdquo;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(155, 82, 'Srijan Lama', 'srijan-lama', NULL, '', '', '<p>&ldquo;Broadway Infosys Nepal= co-operative, friendly team + great infrastructure+ experienced professional instructors+ effective training sessions + guaranteed job placement. This is what I think about Broadway Infosys. I experienced all of these and best of all I got to meet my prospective employer in this great platform. Thank you Broadway. My best wishes are and will always be with Broadway team.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(156, 73, 'Rahul Siwakoti', 'rahul-siwakoti', NULL, '', '', '<p>&ldquo; I am a civil engineering student and I approached Broadway Infosys in CAN Comtech. I was really impressed by the way the counselor responded to my queries and I registered myself right away. I was overwhelmed when I visited Broadway and then got to see my class and received demo training. The, the rest is history. I am really satisfied with the training program and am happy that I am still in touch with my instructor who helps me whenever I need. If anyone would ask me about taking Autocad training, I would surely recommend Broadway based in my experience.&rdquo;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(157, 49, 'Ramila Sapkota', 'ramila-sapkota', NULL, '', '', '<p>&ldquo;I am very happy that I approached Broadway Infosys Nepal for studying Python. I have been searching a proper institute for long who could guide me in this programming language and I finally got introduced with Broadway from one of my friend and ex-student of Broadway. I must say I am really glad with my decision to join Broadway as I got my purpose fulfilled. The instructor is definitely the real time professional as he shared a lot of experiences he had while working in this and pointed out all the considerations I need to take care of which otherwise may have got unnoticed. I am really happy and wish to join Broadway for other IT course soon.&rdquo;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 06:20:59', 0, 0, 1),
(158, 49, 'Bishnu Acharya', 'bishnu-acharya', NULL, '', '', '<p>If there is a great name to remember for IT Training in Nepal, it could not be any other name except Broadway Infosys. &nbsp;Throughout the training periods of Python and Django I got amazing experience in Broadway. The expert trainer lift us easily from the basic level to complex programming within the specified timeframe.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(159, 49, 'Binod Neupane  ', 'binod-neupane', NULL, '', '', '<p>I was searching a best training institution for Python &amp; Django training in Nepal. It&#39;s a high level programming language course. When I was referred to Broadway Infosys Nepal I got to know that it&#39;s the type of Institution that I was seeking since long. I am Thankful to Broadway Infosys Nepal.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(160, 4, 'Rabi Mishra ', 'rabi-mishra', NULL, '', '', '<p>SQL server is familiar to me when I completed my training from Broadway Infosys Nepal. Now I am able to handle bulk numbers of data easily using the techniques I learned. What I felt is: Its Broadway Infosys Nepal that paved the way for my better IT career. Proud to be the part of it !</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(161, 4, 'Kedar Pyakurel ', 'kedar-pyakurel', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway is really as its name to me. I am quite satisfied what I gained from here. The excellent team of Broadway is the exemplary team for IT training. I am able to face the complex challenges in data base after I completed the SQL Server Course from here.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(162, 47, 'Milan Pandey ', 'milan-pandey', NULL, '', '', '<p>My Good career opportunity as Database Administrator and Data Analyst began from MYSQL training I took from Broadway Infosys Nepal. Really I was thankful. As soon as I completed MYSQL training I joined PHP training too. It&#39;s excellent.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(163, 47, 'Rikesh Sainju ', 'rikesh-sainju', NULL, '', '', '<p><br />\r\nBroadway is the best platform to me to transform my career to IT sector. I believe any other institution could not be comparable to Broadway Infosys Nepal. It&#39;s excellent.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(164, 47, 'Yubaraj Dhakal ', 'yubaraj-dhakal', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal to me is the best institution in Nepal in terms of both physical infrastructure and learning environment. I am all the way from Nepalgunj to study here. I felt my choice is perfect.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(165, 6, 'Aman Kumar ', 'aman-kumar', NULL, '', '', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal did a lot for me to establish me as a database professional. I was particularly less familiar to Oracle when I was about to assign my job. Sooner I joined Broadway to grab the opportunity. Within 3 months progression period to my job I become excellent to face the possible challenges on database. All the greetings to Broadway.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(166, 51, 'Manoj Aryal', 'manoj-aryal', NULL, '', '', '<p>Advance Excel Training to me was compulsory when I was joining to INGO for my job. Bulk data sent from our donors should be managed well. I was in trouble. All I get relaxed when I completed Advance Excel Course from Broadway Infosys Nepal. &nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(167, 23, 'Monika Bhatt ', 'monika-bhatt-1', '/uploads/testimonials/1490184077.jpg', '', '', '<p>Studying any kind of IT related training has never been more accessible than it is now. However, amongst the wide range of competitive IT training institutes in Nepal, Broadway Infosys is undoubtedly the best when it comes to understanding and attainment of practical knowledge. The extremely helpful management and teachers, make training feel like a fun filled activity. I highly recommend all graduates to undertake IT related training in Broadway for proper future job prospects.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-22 12:11:01', 0, 0, 1),
(168, 10, 'Diwash sapkota ', 'diwash-sapkota', NULL, '', '', '<p>When I browsed for the best place to learn Graphic designing, the first name I got was Broadway Infosys Nepal. Instantly I contacted broadway and after I analysed the resources and management, I got admitted. Today I am proud to have got guidance from professional teachers and experts. Thank you Broadway!&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-03-26 02:06:49', 0, 0, 1),
(170, 17, 'Sriyansh Subedi  ', 'sriyansh-subedi-1', NULL, '', '', '<p>Getting PHP training in this institute was the best decision ever. I had really genuine experience of learning here. The instructor was superb and the way he taught us with the assigned projects was really impressive. Broadway really has fulfilled it&#39;s promise of providing training with real time professional developers. I received every kind of support and guidance with the whole team of Broadway management. All I can say is a big THANKS!!!!</p>\r\n', '2017-03-26 02:10:29', 0, 0, 1),
(171, 11, 'Prince Yubraaj Karki ', 'prince-yubraaj-karki-1', '/uploads/testimonials/1490495121.png', '', '', '<p>&quot;Knowledge is within your Grasp&quot;<br />\r\nIT related education in Nepal has never been more accessible, and there have never been more options for every type of budget, learning style, and goal. Having so many options under one roof is always great. No doubt, &quot; Broadway infosys&quot; is the only one IT professional institute of Nepal &nbsp;(so far I know) where more than 75 IT related courses are available to start. As soon as I heard about the Broadway infosys while I was in California,USA. I started to find out more information and former students&#39; reviews about this institute and I finally made a decision to start my IT career from this institute. The Broadway Infosys experience is a lifelong one that I will never forget for the rest of my life! It was fruitful, intensive, worthy, challenging, informative, enlightening, comprehensive, instructive, and unforgettable.I learned a lot of things that I can use in my professional life and had loads of fun at the same time. Every single thing about Broadway was amazing. I truly had a great experience at Broadway infosys while learning there C, C++, Web Design and QA.<br />\r\nIn fact, It&#39;s always hard to take decision when you have to decide where to pursue your goals. It&rsquo;s a big decision, and it can be hard to find quality and pertinent information to help you on your way. The instructors I had were great, qualified, very knowledgeable and I learned more than I have ever expected. Furthermore, I have many friends who also attended the Broadway infosys in the past and they are all doing very well. What&#39;s more! Broadway infosys give their students a platform in which to get their foot in the door.<br />\r\nI am incredibly satisfied. It is worth the time, money and energy. For this reason, I have written my experience, hoping that It would surely benefit to the new student.<br />\r\nAll in all, I had a great experience at the Broadway Infosys and I would definitely recommend it to anyone who has the enthusiasm for learning and is keen on self development or make progress in the IT related field or any students who are genuinely focusing to land their career in the field of IT.<br />\r\n&quot;Great management, great staffs, great place, thumbs up &nbsp;&quot;<br />\r\nGod bless you all.</p>\r\n', '2017-03-26 02:25:21', 0, 0, 1);
