(1, 1, 'Bikesh Manandhar', 'bikesh-manandhar', '/uploads/testimonials/1478747088.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal, the ultimate place, where I have learned Web-designing. I joined this institute and learned the Web-designing course in the friendly environment. Really, this institute provides the better education as it provides different computer courses and is instructed by the reputed and well trained teachers. Instructors are also frank. Everyone would easily get desired computer courses at the cheap price, yet so qualitative education. I got the opportunity to join Broadway Infosys Nepal and was able to broad my knowledge in the field of Web-Designing. Thank you Broadway!</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(2, 7, 'Dirga Raj Lama', 'dirga-raj-lama', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-size: small; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal, in my opinion, is that perfect path where the students are provided with quality education in computer technology. It was one of my greatest investment decisions that I have chosen Broadway Infosys for completing my computer skills with web designing and web programming. The fabulous Institution environment always motivates me to learn something new in computer IT courses. The teachers and their teaching methodology are quite spacious and helpful in developing my computer IT skills. The people here are very friendly. Management of this Institution is good. So their efforts play vital role to secure practical knowledge and develop good skills. Thus, if you have strength, opportunity is behind you. Broadway Infosys Nepal provides that opportunity to achieve success in your life.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(3, 7, 'Suvanno Tharu', 'suvanno-tharu', '/uploads/_thumbs/Images/testimonials/su.png', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal, a complete institution for learners. As a student of Broadway Infosys Nepal, I can proudly say that this is the place where students can learn with friendly environment. Another plus point of Broadway Infosys Nepal is good management, you don&#39;t have to complain, they research and manage what you need before you complain. When I first came to Broadway Infosys Nepal, I thought this institute is also the same as the other institutes but when I talked to the management and came to know about its teaching environment, I was impressed and I joined Broadway Infosys Nepal on the spot. I am fully satisfied with Broadway Infosys Nepal because of its quality education with dedicated teachers and peaceful friendly environment. Broadway Infosys Nepal makes me successful and I am happy to say that Broadway Infosys Nepal is the BEST.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(4, 2, 'Loday Phuntsho', 'loday-phuntsho', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 1px;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal has got very welll talented teachers. And, if I talk about my teacher, he is very much friendly to ask. So we can interact with him very well. We could solve the doubt of ours. Broadway infosys Nepal has got very well management. I would suggest to carry on with the same management which will be more beneficial also for the foreigner students.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(5, 3, 'Karma Leki', 'karma-leki', '', '<p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal is an&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://broadwayinfosys.com/it-education.php\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 149, 200); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\" title=\"it training center in Nepal\">IT training company</a><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\"> ;yet, good enough to gain knowledge .The staff are so friendly and nice. Teachers are full of knowledge and helps us to grab the knowledge in each and every possible ways.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(6, 1, 'Suraj Adhikari', 'suraj-adhikari', '/uploads/_thumbs/Images/Suraj%20Adhikari.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys is the BEST as well as an awesome institute for IT in Nepal. It has given me a lot to think about and pursue my career as a Software Engineer. I&#39;m a web developer and I think this is the best institute for anyone who is searching and even thinking to take his/her first step in IT or software development.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(7, 7, 'Makh Bahadur Gurung', 'makh-bahadur-gurung', '', '<p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">According to my opinion,I think&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal</strong><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;is the right place where we can learn more than our expectation. Broadway provides highly expert trainer and well neat and clean class environments. In short&nbsp; &quot;east or west </span><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal</strong><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;is the best&quot;. - Mak Gurung</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(8, 1, 'Manesh Timilsina', 'manesh-timilsina', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px;\">I want to thank Broadway Infosys Nepal for providing such skills and training for students like us. I found teachers here so friendly and whole learning environment very suitable to encourage us to learn properly. Its only because of Broadway Infosys Nepal that I got first step of success to built my career as PHP programmer as well as Web Designer. Once again thank you Broadway. -Er. Manesh Timilsina</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(9, 1, 'Niraj Shakya', 'niraj-shakya', '', '<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\">I had many choices to select IT Institution for my training in PHP Programming. But when I came to know about&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal</strong>&nbsp;I immediately joined it. Now after the completion of course, I can say I did the right thing in choosing Broadway Infosys Nepal because I can now independently do the programming in PHP.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\">I want to thank management team and particularly instructor of PHP Programming of&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Broadway Infosys Nepal</strong>&nbsp;for all the help they provided during the period of the course. I want to emphasize that even after the completion of the course they are so helpful that whenever I need some guidance they are always available for me. So I highly recommend Broadway Infosys Nepal for IT Training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Er. Niraj Shakya</strong></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(10, 7, 'Sajan Kafle', 'sajan-kafle', '', '<p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">I am an IT P</span><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">rofessional Officer</strong><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">. All the merits of my IT life belongs to Broadway Infosys Nepal . Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the most famous institution in Information Technology field. I have simply these words to say</span><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;about Broadway &nbsp;&quot;East or west Broadway is the best</strong><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">&quot;.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\" />\r\n<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; word-spacing: 1px; font-size: 11px; text-align: justify;\">Er. Sajan Kafle</strong></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(11, 7, 'Dipendra Thapa', 'dipendra-thapa', '', '<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\">&quot; If your main vision is to gain a professional and&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">job oriented training on web designing,then Broadway Infosys is the right place for you</strong>. You will get more than what you have expected through their&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">training program and won&#39;t regret your decision</strong>. After a month of finishing my training on professional web designing, I got a job on Sofos Software and worked there for three months.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Now, I am currently working as a Freelancer Web designer&nbsp;</strong>and has been quite satisfied for where I am now. The credit goes to all the team of&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" title=\"Computer training Nepal\">Broadway Infosys</strong>. And, I am sure to choose<a href=\"http://broadwayinfosys.com/\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 149, 200);\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Computer training institute in kathmandu Nepal\">&nbsp;Broadway Infosys Nepal</a>&nbsp;for any future training that I may wish to take. &quot;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(12, 8, 'Sadhana Rijal Khatri Chettri', 'sadhana-rijal-khatri-chettri', '', '<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\">I am very happy that I chose&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" title=\"Advance training center in kathmandu Nepal\">Broadway Infosys Nepal&nbsp;</strong>for my training in QA. Here, I found experienced instructor; not just a teacher in the field of QA. The management is also very satisfying and &nbsp;always ready to help the students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"padding: 5px 15px 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; color: rgb(24, 53, 68);\">I would surely prefer Broadway Infosys Nepal in future for any IT related professional training programs. BIN is an institute that is purely focused on providing professional IT training to its desiring students.&nbsp;<strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">I wish all the very best for BIN</strong>.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(13, 1, 'Sanjeeb Thapa', 'sanjeeb-thapa', '', '<p>After visiting Broadway Infosys Nepal, I recognized myself to be a deterministic and a skillful person. Whilst in waiting, I enrolled for the &quot;Advance PHP/MYSQL&quot; programme which felt like the perfect fit to complement my programming experience and developing my programming skill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAt the end of the course ,it dawned on me that I was now empowered with the skills, knowledge to set up and operate and work as a qualified PHP Programmer. Backed with confidence and courage I just could not wait to complete the program, I was enrolled in Web Development Company within a week after completion of my course. I found the course relevant to standard IT industry requirement.<br />\r\nThere were times when I wanted to grow particularly in developing my skill on PHP and I found my lecturer empowering me a way to success. This is when I found it important and helpful to reassure myself and look at the big picture to re-energies to go on. Again the Key was set to Broadway Infosys Nepal. I am currently working at Eastlink Technologies Tripureswor, Nepal Pos: Mid level PHP Programmer/web developer.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(14, 1, 'Suvasini Shrestha', 'suvasini-shrestha', '', '<p>I felt that I was taught on practical which turned out to be very good for us. I am thankful to Broadway Infosys Nepal for arranging our classes as per our suitable time.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(15, 5, 'Ankita Pradhan', 'ankita-pradhan', '', '<p>I feel lucky to have joined Broadway Infosys Nepal .It is the best in its kind. I have got all my queries fulfilled here. I never had any problem to ask any question in related subject.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(16, 1, 'Sakar Aryal', 'sakar-aryal', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 1px;\">It feels great when teacher provides such a friendly atmosphere. I have also gained the confidence to work on web development after my classes here.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(17, 1, 'Govinda Joshi', 'govinda-joshi', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 1px;\">It feels so good after the completion of my PHP &amp; Mysql course here in Broadway Infosys Nepal. Due to the friendly behavior and the practical approach, I think I can project any work on the subject successfully.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(18, 7, 'Dambar Kumar Khatri', 'dambar-kumar-khatri', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 1px;\">Best IT training institute among all other I have heard of and experienced till now.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(19, 1, 'Prem Dhoj Moktan', 'prem-dhoj-moktan', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 1px;\">Our teacher was very interactive and friendly with a very unique and understandable teaching technique. He makes the students very comfortable.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
(20, 6, 'Jayendra Kunwar', 'jayendra-kunwar', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(24, 53, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify; word-spacing: 1px;\">Teacher was excellent in his teaching and instructions and the management of Broadway Infosys Nepal provided us with utmost moral support. I am currently engaged as a Database Management Instructor which I believe is due to Broadway Infosys Nepal.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:15', 1),
