(100, 1, 'Shiva Kumar Shrestha ', 'shiva-kumar-shrestha', '/uploads/gallery/forandroid/sh.jpg', '<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Review\">\r\n<div itemprop=\"name\">\r\n<p>Broadway Infosys is no. 1 php training institute in Nepal.<br />\r\nBroadway Infosys Nepal is the best IT Training Center in Nepal. If you really want to learn or gain sth about recent technology practically at affordable cost then Broadway is the best option for you. During my training, classes, interaction, etc I found this institution very co-operative too.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(101, 5, 'Rishikesh Mandal', 'rishikesh-mandal', '/uploads/Rishikesh%20%20Mandal(1).jpg', '<p>I found the same learning environment here, which I had expected before joining this institute. Supportive and friendly nature of our sir really helped us to clarify even the simplest doubt without any hesitation. Teaching methodology like coming up with different example for all the topics and subtopics was really impressive. I hope all my classmate might have benefited enough from this. I feel I was well co-operated here at Broadway and hope for the same co-operation further.<br />\r\nThank you.<br />\r\nSincerely&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(102, 50, 'Aviskar  Basnet ', 'aviskar-basnet', '/uploads/basnet.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is the best academy for hard working students who wants to sharpen their skills to make a good start in IT career. The teachers here expertise in their core subject matter &amp; are highly experienced professionals. So, students can get quality professional education at affordable cost. The teachers are really hard working &amp; keep updating themselves time by time to provide the knowledge based on latest technology. Environment at Broadway is good &amp; positive. Anyone will adore this environment &amp; it helps them to motivate to the right path. Broadway members &amp; teachers are always ready to give any kind of possible support for students. Broadway provides internships &amp; job placement for eligible students as it has cooperated with most of the IT companies in Nepal. There are lots of good aspects of Broadway from which students can take more &amp; more advantages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nWhat I gained at Broadway<br />\r\nBefore joining the Broadway, everything on IT field was like puzzle for me. After I joined Broadway, day by day I started to figure out the IT field. I have completed Responsive Web Designing Training &amp; JAVA Development Training at Broadway. Broadway helped me a lot to give a good start to my IT career. Now, I&rsquo;m one of the effective employer at my company because of the knowledge &amp; skills that I gained from Broadway. Broadway members &amp; teachers always motivated me to be the best. I&rsquo;ve never studied in friendly environment like here. I always want to be student at Broadway &amp; I&rsquo;m planning to take some more trainings at Broadway. Even now teachers are ready to solve my problems related to the academic topic. I really thank a lot to the Broadway members &amp; teachers for their great supportive role. I&rsquo;m proud to be the student of Broadway.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(103, 50, 'Yuvraj Bashyal', 'yuvraj-bashyal', '/uploads/pic.jpg', '<p>&ldquo;Coming to Broadway Infosys Nepal was the best thing that I had ever done!&rdquo; I found the management team of Broadway Infosys Nepal seeking for the bright future of their student and translating its plans for the overall development of student. I loved how the teacher&#39;s approached the students and especially loved how Broadway made us feel like we were part of the family. My experience at this IT centre has truly been a remarkable one. Thanks to Broadway Infosys for providing confidence in my abilities. &ldquo;Thank You&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
