(105, 21, 'Hem Raj Bhatta ', 'hem-raj-bhatta', '/uploads/hem(2).jpg', '<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Review\">\r\n<div itemprop=\"name\">If you searching Professional IT training center for WordPress Training, you have to join BROADWAY INFOSYS NEPAL<br />\r\nBroadway Infosys Nepal is an interesting school, the teachers are very nice and they teach in a really good way to prepare the students. The teachers here expertise in their core subject matter &amp; are highly experienced professionals. If you searching Professional IT training center you have to join BROADWAY INFOSYS NEPAL. It is a wonderful experience!</div>\r\n\r\n<div itemprop=\"name\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div itemprop=\"reviewBody\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(106, 34, 'Vivek Ratna Kansakar', 'vivek-ratna-kansakar', '/uploads/Vivek%20Ratna%20Kansakar.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the professional institute for learning coding. The teachers in Broadway are expert in their respective fields and easy to communicate with. The learning/training method is also interactive and the learning environment is also good &amp; positive. Broadway also provides job placement feature for its eligible students at renowned IT companies in Nepal. I studied Laravel Framework and have gained a great deal of knowledge from this institute and also have joined a reputable company through Broadway. I suggest Broadway to anyone who wants to learn Web Development for job purpose. Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(107, 5, 'AJUSHA RIZAL', 'ajusha-rizal', '/uploads/testimonials/AJUSHA%20RIZAL%20teat.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys is the gateway to enter the IT software industry. I should specifically mention the support given to me by the faculty. The curriculum is well-structured and matches real-time projects. It is updated and their lab facility is an added advantage where we can acquire practical knowledge. I also want to take this opportunity to thank our teacher Mr. Yadav Raj Ojha for such wonderful class. You have been so direct and so honest in teaching us vital information about important issues that revolve around the IT field. You have made it so constructive and easy to learn in that it truly has made a difference in the way I look at programming now. Thank you for a wonderful support Broadway Infosys Nepal .</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(108, 5, 'Jagat Man Mulguthi ', 'jagat-man-mulguthi', '/uploads/testimonials/jagat%20testi.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal , as name implies it is a high way to get trained in technological skills. Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the leading and successful IT training institutes that have satisfied all of the IT enthusiast&rsquo;s students to acquire various IT skills. I joined the Broadway in 2012 for Web Development Training and till now I have trained here with many IT skills. One of my favorite things that attracts me all the time is: the friendly management and expert IT Instructors. Aside from educating me in IT skills, Broadway Infosys Nepal&nbsp;has counseled and has assisted me in acquiring getting job. However comes to me for IT training, Broadway Infosys Nepal is my first list of selection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(109, 5, 'Anil kr Sah ', 'anil-kr-sah', '/uploads/testimonials/Anil%20testi%20-min.jpg', '<p>The future depends on what you do today. I feel Broadway Infosys Nepal &nbsp;as a bridge way between my Academic life to career life. The most important aspect of Broadway Infosys Nepal is its teachers and management.Teachers are very friendly and professionals. I feel proud joining Broadway Infosys Nepal &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(110, 2, 'Jen Bati', 'jen-bati', '/uploads/testimonials/Jen%20Bati-min.jpg', '<p>Gaining professional skills in Microsoft .Net programming language (C#, ASP.NET, MS-SQL) at this fine institution was a boon for me.<br />\r\nI have been Several IT Academic overseas and in Nepal. Which I search internet and find out this Broad ways info IT Instituted, I though more comfortable and Quality Latest technology tools with Specialist teacher Multiple software Development teachers Compare to Other It Institute. I took Advance Web Designing, Advance Wordpress and Advance SEO (Search Engine Optimization) Development from broadways infosys Nepal IT Instituted. I am thinking More Multiple course again. And who is interest learn IT field and take better training. I am I highly Recommend Broadway infosys Nepal. Thank you for all Broadways Infosys Nepal Team.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(111, 5, 'Sanjok  Khakurel ', 'sanjok-khakurel', '/uploads/testimonials/sanjok%20ji%20web-min.jpg', '<p>Java training in Nepal by <strong>Broadway Infosys</strong> is one of the best in the country. I truly believe that Broadway Infosys Nepal is a &ldquo;Broadway Infosys Nepal&rdquo; where fresher college graduates, absolute beginners and other personalities can walk to go to their ultimate destination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After completion of the course I found myself into a new level of programming world. Well organized and knowledge oriented course, highly qualified and experienced trainer, well maintained lab and peaceful environment has really given me new courage insight and energy to reach up to my destination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is an experience that will live long in my memory. I want to express my gratitude to Mr. Yadav Raj Ojha for carrying through Challenging program enough effectively. Thank you for the opportunity and warm support Broadway Infosys Nepal family.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(112, 7, 'Rabin Gurung', 'rabin-gurung', '/uploads/testimonials/rabin%20web-min.jpg', '<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Review\">\r\n<div itemprop=\"name\">Web design training in Broadway Infosys Nepal has been one of the best choice for my career.<br />\r\nI have been Several IT Academic overseas and in Nepal. Which I search internet and find out this Broadway s infosys IT Instituted, I though more comfortable and Quality Latest technology tools with Specialist teacher Multiple software Development teachers Compare to Other It Institute. I took Advance Web Designing, Advance Wordpress and Advance SEO (Search Engine Optimization) Development from broadway infosys Nepal IT Instituted. I am thinking More Multiple course again. And who is interest learn IT field and take better training. I am I highly Recommend Broadway infosys Nepal. Thank you for all Broadways Infosys Nepal Team.</div>\r\n\r\n<div itemprop=\"name\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(113, 39, 'Rekha Bohara', 'rekha-bohara', '/uploads/testimonials/rekha%20web%20page.jpg', '<p>In IT field where if anything that &nbsp;matter most &nbsp;is skill , Being IT student I always have passion towards programming and Broadway Infosys turn my that passion &nbsp;into skill. To choose Broadway &nbsp;is one of my best decision. 24/7 running classes on each and every new technology, amazing &nbsp; Managerial management skill of Uttam sir, best management team .selected best experience teacher, I &nbsp;found Broadway more than my expectations. they don&#39;t only help you to sharpen your skill but also help you to establish your career in best companies around the world. At first I &nbsp;came Broadway empty hand holding &nbsp;passion for IOS but in return I found hand full of opportunities . Broadway help me to step my career path in professional world . It turn my dream into reality.It provides young fresh students a platform &nbsp;to rise their skill and &nbsp;achieve their dreams. I really appreciate how they are doing. I&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nRekha Bohara<br />\r\nIOS mobile application Training&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(114, 1, 'Feroz Siwakoti', 'feroz-siwakoti', '/uploads/testimonials/Feroz%20Siwakoti%20web%20(1).jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is one of the Pioneer IT learning institute. The methods and approach of teaching in Broadway is very commendable. The institute provides a definite productive gateway by interlinking the bridge between the learned foundations in college academics to the real world industrial applicable projects.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(115, 34, 'Yamendra Pun ', 'yamendra-pun', '/uploads/testimonials/pun%20web%20.jpg', '<p>If you are looking for professional IT training, then Broadway Infosys Nepal &nbsp;is the best. I had an opportunity to learn Laravel Framework at Broadway Infosys Nepal. I found the teachers are supportive and friendly so learning is always fun. The teaching methods at BIN is industry oriented and the best practices used by current IT Companies. I would like to thanks our instructor for his exceptional time and effort to make our class more professional. He is always willing to teach new things and help us in every way possible. Apart from this Broadway Infosys Nepal has best management team. They are always willing to help and guide you. I feel so proud to be part of Broadway Infosys Nepal family.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(116, 7, 'Roshan Tamang', 'roshan-tamang', '/uploads/testimonials/Roshan%20Tamang.jpg', '<p>To Broadway Infosys Nepal,<br />\r\nIn order to utilize the three months of gap after my SLC examination, I was in great confusion what to do. My all other friends already had joined bridge courses language classes and some basic computer classes. I felt like I was in too last among my friends. I wanted to develop some IT skills in that period. Therefore, I spent many times in search of computer training institute in Kathmandu. I found a unique institute named &lsquo;Broadway Infosys Nepal&rsquo; when I searched for the institute. Its responsive website fascinated me. Then the testimonials of ex-students inspired me to join Broadway.<br />\r\nThe journey of two months with Broadway in Web Design and C&amp; c++ Programming was unforgettable and very interesting. Qualified and experienced instructors led me to perfection in my related field. I&rsquo;m highly satisfied with each and every moment spent with Broadway. Fast internet and 24 hours power supply played very important contribution for the training. It helped to run the practical activities along with learning theoretical knowledge&rsquo;s. Perfect guidance, feedback and interaction of my teachers made me feel like home and I&rsquo;m being taught by my own friends. I didn&rsquo;t get notice of spending two months with Broadway.<br />\r\nFor new students or people who want to gain or improve their IT skill, I want to advise them to join Broadway. It is the team of qualified, professional and experienced instructors and staff. It gives quality of knowledge and guides perfectly to way of related IT field where you want to make your career at moderate payment. It offers various subjects like Web Design, AutoCAD, Java, Android etc.. It not only gives knowledge, it offers for internships or jobs after training for the students.<br />\r\nI&rsquo;m proud of being a student of Broadway Infosys Nepal. I liked its all facilities and hope for all the best in the future. Keep it up.<br />\r\nThank you.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(117, 5, 'Rishabh Jha', 'rishabh-jha', '/uploads/testimonials/Rishabweb%20jha.jpg', '<p>In IT field if anything that matter most is extra skill, being a B. tech Computer science student I always have<br />\r\nPassion towards programming and Broadway Infosys turn me &nbsp; in that passion into a skill.<br />\r\nTo choose Broadway is one of my best decision 24/7 running classes on each and every new technology! Skilled &amp; friendly teachers.<br />\r\nThe difference between extra ordinary &amp; ordinary is that little &quot;extra &ldquo;so to be an extraordinary<br />\r\nJoin today &amp; get an opportunity to be as more than you know or as u are capable off!<br />\r\nAs I joined java language by empty set &amp; attempted it<br />\r\nNow I could understand the difference between ordinary &amp; extra ordinary!</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(118, 2, 'SOMNATH SHARMA', 'somnath-sharma', '/uploads/testimonials/som%20web%20.jpg', '<p>Broadway Infosys Nepal is the Best institute for IT training in Nepal. Where we can learn more than our expectation. It provides highly expert trainer as well as friendly and clean environment. I found Broadway Infosys Nepal<br />\r\nPath to my Success full Carrier.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(119, 5, 'Pratikshya Adhikari', 'pratikshya-adhikari', '/uploads/testimonials/Pratikshya%20Adhikar%201i.jpg', '<p>I had a dream to be successful programmer in java and now I can see my future bright with help of Broadway Infosys. It is said that good shoe is needed to walk and only few can recognize it. So, in that case, Broadway Infosys is a good shoe with very good , friendly studying environment which lead us to the successful path.<br />\r\nI studying JAVA feel very proud to be part of this institute and also want to thank Broadway Infosys for making me skilled and confident in todays competitive market field.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(120, 22, 'Abish Ojha', 'abish-ojha', '/uploads/testimonials/abish1.jpg', '<p>I first found out about Broadway Infosys 4 years back when I was not sure where and how do I implement my theoretical knowledge. Then, Broadway provided me the push to succeed in real world. I do not need to mention again and again that Broadway Infosys is one of the best Institution to groom into professional world.<br />\r\nBroadway Infosys is one of the biggest names as an institution for a reason. I did specific courses there which provided me with practical knowledge of how the work is actually done in real world and the courses&#39; focus on real world.<br />\r\nI am recommending Broadway Infosys because it somehow gave me the direction and pushed me into the professional life, where I worked as Java Developer for 2 years and now am working at IT Department in Sanima Bank.&nbsp;<br />\r\nSo basically, as per my experience and success, I can and will recommend Broadway Infosys Nepal without any hesitation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(121, 39, 'Bibek Karki', 'bibek-karki', '/uploads/testimonials/bibek11.jpg', '<p><span class=\"_5yl5\"><span>I have been around broadway (well, in times) since my college days 4/5 years earlier. And according to my experiences, there is ALWAYS a huge void in between academic education and the industrial requirements. Broadway simply bridges that gap and provides professional training that in itself acts as a stepping stone towards the future career. Moreover, trainings provided here are solely by industrial experts themselves, therefore totally reliable! Training in itself is a never ending process, I mean - as a programmer, you begin with C/C++, then html/css, then web stuffs like php/asp, and so on. The train simply never stops and thanks broadway for being there at the right hour. Apart from that, timing here is so flexible, I mean you are a student, right? - then fine, you can have broadways after college hours. You are a professional? Then fine again. You can always be here before or after work. In short, suit yourself and learn steadily and comfortably. Having learnt ios here simply provided me a wonderful opportunity to upscale my professional skills to a whole new dimension. Now I can completely go full stack in mobile apps development. Finally, I would also like to hugely thank our ios lecturer for being nice and friendly and for providing technical assistance whenever needed. Broadway simply walks its talks. Thank you very much broadway for successfully delivering your promises.</span></span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(122, 5, 'Suman Koju', 'suman-koju', '/uploads/testimonials/suman%20koju%20web.jpg', '<p>I&#39;m very thankful to you sir. Your support has given me a kind of inspiration. I got an appointment as an intern in an IT company in Bhaktapur as PHP developer with reference of my projects. And of course, all credits goes to you and Broadway. But they want 20 hours of mine in a week as intern. So although I got appointment, I&#39;m thinking whether to join or not due to time inconvenience. After all, I got to know that now I can get appointments. It&#39;s all because of you and Broadway. Thank you so much sir once again. Really feeling happy.</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(123, 3, 'Suman Yaakmi', 'suman-yaakmi', '/uploads/testimonials/suman%20yakami11.jpg', '<p>Learning at Broadway Infosys Nepal is the best decision I&#39;ve ever made. Broadway has helped me in achievement of my career goal and to compete in the world of IT. I am very thankful to the excellent team of trainers that gave me the knowledge and confidence and has brought a new dimension into my life to achieve a successful career. I had completed Advanced PHP session and Microsoft .Net package (C#.net, Asp.net, MS-SQL) and want to learn more. I would strongly recommend Broadway Infosys Nepal to anyone who wants to start and excel their career in IT as it is the best IT training institute in Nepal.<br />\r\nThank you Broadway !!!</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(124, 5, 'PRAKASH BIST', 'prakash-bist', '/uploads/testimonials/prakash%20web.jpg', '<p><span class=\"_5yl5\">I choose to learn from the best. When it comes to learning how to code, Broadway is the place where I find freedom to learn coding. I have always had an interest in working as a java programmer. I consider myself extremely fortunate that I made the choice to study java programming at Broadway. It has always been encouraging to learn beyond the abilities and for me Broadway has played substantial role in my career development. Obviously, I would like to say that Broadway is the institution where I learned career oriented knowledge in very short period of time. The skills I have gained through the course have equipped me to accomplish my professional goal. I would like to thank the entire Broadway family for providing such a wonderful platform for people like me. I hope it continues to produce more professionals in the days ahead.</span></p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(125, 17, 'RAVI SHARMA BASTOLA', 'ravi-sharma-bastola', '/uploads/uploads/rrrrr(2).jpg', 'BroadWay Infosys is the only institute in Nepal where you learn the techniques to tackle the problem. The main focus in Broadway Infosys is to solve the problem with creativity instead of copying the solution. I wanted to start an IT career but did not know where to start. Broadway gave me the platform from where I began to see my career clearly and I am thankful to them for that. All of the staff , the teachers are helpful and the teaching techniques are reviewed on the monthly basis by the teachers to meet the latest demands of the industry. I hope Broadway will continuously help students reach their desired careers as they did to me . Thanks To BROADWAY INFOSYS NEPAL\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1),
(126, 21, 'PRAMOD THAKUR', 'pramod-thakur', '/uploads/uploads/pramod%20web(2).jpg', '<p>First of all , I am very very thankful to my teacher who taught me. He is a very good teacher of PHP development. His teaching style is very simple, conceptual, logical and more effective. He always smiles in difficult situation and handles problem in easy way. He always guides the latest concept and new technology. So thanks for not making us learn the way you wanted to teach, but teaching us the way we wanted to learn. I think &quot;Technology has made it easier for students to learn with new devices , but nothing can come close to the experience of being taught by an inspirational teacher like him&quot;.<br />\r\nBroadway Infosys Nepal is a No.1 training center in Nepal; they always launch new professional skills as well as more effective, conceptual and dynamic teachers. They always help those students who want to improve their professional skills. I have heard Broadway Infosys Nepal giving job opportunity to deserving students, yes they give but at the same time, Broadway Infosys Nepal gives good quality study to their students. I am feeling very proud and lucky to join Broadway Infosys Nepal. So thanks for going out of your way and teaching me life&rsquo;s lessons which I have never learnt from textbooks and reference books. Thanks to all members of Broadway Infosys Nepal who guided me, taught me and gave me a big opportunity and heartily thanks to Mr. Utam Adhikari</p>\r\n', '2017-01-02 11:27:17', 1);
